(3, 'Divino Espírito Santo', '2013-05-01', 'SANTO_14022017115812_1.jpg', 'de 25 de abril a 01 de maio', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">No&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cristianismo\" title=\"Cristianismo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">cristianismo</a>, o&nbsp;<b>Espírito Santo</b>&nbsp;é a terceira&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prosopon\" title=\"Prosopon\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">prosopon</a></i>&nbsp;da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sant%C3%ADssima_Trindade\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Santíssima Trindade\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Santíssima Trindade</a>&nbsp;- juntamente com&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deus_Pai\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Deus Pai\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Deus Pai</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deus_Filho\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Deus Filho\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Deus Filho</a>&nbsp;- e é o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deus\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"Deus\">Deus</a>&nbsp;onipotente<sup id=\"cite_ref-Erickson103_1-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-Erickson103-1\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[1]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Hammond_2-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-Hammond-2\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[2]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-cathhs_3-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-cathhs-3\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[3]</a></sup>. Ele é visto como sendo uma das pessoas do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deus_Triuno\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Deus Triuno\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Deus Triuno</a>, que revelou seu Santo Nome&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/YHWH\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"YHWH\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">YHWH</a>&nbsp;ao seu povo em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Israel\" title=\"Israel\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Israel</a>, enviou seu Filho Eternamente Gerado&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jesus\" title=\"Jesus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Jesus</a>&nbsp;para salvá-los da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Retribui%C3%A7%C3%A3o_divina&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Retribuição divina (página não existe)\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 88, 88); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">fúria divina</a>&nbsp;e enviou o Espírito Santo para santificar e dar vida à sua Igreja<sup id=\"cite_ref-Catholic_Catechism_Holy_Name_4-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-Catholic_Catechism_Holy_Name-4\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[4]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Summa_Theologica_Procession_of_Divine_Persons_5-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-Summa_Theologica_Procession_of_Divine_Persons-5\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[5]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Mystici_Corporis_Christi_6-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-Mystici_Corporis_Christi-6\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[6]</a></sup>. O Deus Triuno se manifesta como três \"pessoas\" (<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grego_koin%C3%A9\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Grego koiné\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">grego koiné</a>:&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hypostasis\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hypostasis\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">hypostasis</a></i>)<sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-7\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[7]</a></sup>&nbsp;de uma única substância divina (<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grego_antigo\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Grego antigo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">grego antigo</a>:&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ousia\" title=\"Ousia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">ousia</a></i>)<sup id=\"cite_ref-Systematic_theology_8-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-Systematic_theology-8\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[8]</a></sup>, chamada&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deus_no_cristianismo\" title=\"Deus no cristianismo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Deus</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Catholic_Catechism_Trinity_9-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-Catholic_Catechism_Trinity-9\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[9]</a></sup>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jesus\" title=\"Jesus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Jesus</a>&nbsp;é apresentado nos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evangelhos\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Evangelhos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Evangelhos</a>&nbsp;como sendo o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Messias\" title=\"Messias\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Messias</a>&nbsp;há muito profetizado, que batiza não com água, mas com o \"Espírito Santo\" e com fogo (<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Lucas/III#3:16\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/Lucas/III\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Lucas 3:16</a>). Antes da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paix%C3%A3o_de_Cristo\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Paixão de Cristo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Paixão</a>, durante a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%9Altima_Ceia\" title=\"Última Ceia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Última Ceia</a>, Ele promete enviar do Pai outro&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Par%C3%A1clito\" title=\"Paráclito\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Paráclito</a>&nbsp;ao mundo, o Espírito Santo, o \"<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_da_Verdade\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Espírito da Verdade\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Espírito da Verdade</a>\" (<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Jo%C3%A3o/XV#15:26\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/João/XV\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">João 15:26</a>), que, segundo os&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atos_dos_Ap%C3%B3stolos\" title=\"Atos dos Apóstolos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Atos dos Apóstolos</a>, apareceu na forma de \"línguas de fogo\" sobre os&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disc%C3%ADpulos\" class=\"mw-redirect mw-disambig\" title=\"Discípulos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">discípulos</a>, os&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ap%C3%B3stolos\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Apóstolos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">apóstolos</a>, durante o evento conhecido como&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pentecostes\" title=\"Pentecostes\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Pentecostes</a>, que marca o início da Igreja de Jesus na Terra (<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Atos/II#2:1\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/Atos/II\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Atos 2:1</a>).</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">A compreensão do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mist%C3%A9rio_da_Sant%C3%ADssima_Trindade\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mistério da Santíssima Trindade\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">mistério da Santíssima Trindade</a>&nbsp;varia nas diversas&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Denomina%C3%A7%C3%B5es_crist%C3%A3s\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Denominações cristãs\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">denominações cristãs</a>. Algumas se intitulam&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trinitarismo\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Trinitarismo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">trinitárias</a>&nbsp;por compartilharem o ponto de vista majoritário acima, enquanto que as&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antitrinitarismo\" title=\"Antitrinitarismo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">não trinitárias</a>&nbsp;têm compreensão diferente do papel do Espírito Santo. Mesmo entre os trinitários, há diferenças: enquanto que as&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igrejas_Cat%C3%B3licas_Orientais\" title=\"Igrejas Católicas Orientais\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Igrejas Católicas Orientais</a>&nbsp;e a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Ortodoxa\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"Igreja Ortodoxa\">Igreja Ortodoxa</a>&nbsp;afirmam que o Espírito procede apenas do Pai (\"através do Filho\"), a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Cat%C3%B3lica\" title=\"Igreja Católica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Igreja Católica</a>&nbsp;mantém que o Espírito Santo procede tanto do Pai quanto do Filho, uma doutrina que ficou conhecida como&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Filioque\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Filioque\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Filioque</a></i>&nbsp;e já foi tema de grande controvérsia.</p><h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 1em 0px 0.25em; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(162, 169, 177); font-size: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;Linux Libertine&quot;, Georgia, Times, serif; line-height: 1.3;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Etimologia\">Etimologia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: Etimologia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Editar secção: Etimologia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar código-fonte</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">]</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">A palavra&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%C3%ADngua_grega\" title=\"Língua grega\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">grega</a>&nbsp;<i>pneuma</i>&nbsp;<b>??????</b>&nbsp;geralmente significa \"espírito\" e é encontrada por volta de 385 vezes no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Novo_Testamento\" title=\"Novo Testamento\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Novo Testamento</a>&nbsp;e a palavra grega \"Agion\" Geralmente Significa \"Santo\", com acadêmicos discordando entre 3 e 9 casos<sup id=\"cite_ref-KJVL_10-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-KJVL-10\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[10]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-11\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[11]</a></sup>. A utilização varia: em 133 casos, ele se refere ao \"espírito\" de forma geral, em 153 ao termo \"espiritual\" e, possivelmente, se refira ao Espírito Santo em 93 casos<sup id=\"cite_ref-KJVL_10-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-KJVL-10\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[10]</a></sup>. Nuns poucos, o termo pode significar também \"sopro\" ou \"vida\" em Hebraico \"Ruach\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-KJVL_10-2\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-KJVL-10\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[10]</a></sup>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">A&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teologia\" title=\"Teologia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">teologia</a>&nbsp;do Espírito Santo é chamada de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pneumatologia\" title=\"Pneumatologia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">pneumatologia</a>.</p><h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 1em 0px 0.25em; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(162, 169, 177); font-size: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;Linux Libertine&quot;, Georgia, Times, serif; line-height: 1.3;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Juda.C3.ADsmo\">Judaísmo</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: Judaísmo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Editar secção: Judaísmo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar código-fonte</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">]</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">O termo \"espírito santo\" aparece apenas três vezes na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/B%C3%ADblia_Hebraica\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bíblia Hebraica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Bíblia Hebraica</a>&nbsp;(em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Salmos/LI#51:11\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/Salmos/LI\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Salmos 51:11</a>&nbsp;e duas vezes em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Isa%C3%ADas/LXIII#63:10\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/Isaías/LXIII\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Isaías 63:10-11</a>)<sup id=\"cite_ref-Millsxi_12-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-Millsxi-12\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[12]</a></sup>. No&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juda%C3%ADsmo\" title=\"Judaísmo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">judaísmo</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shema\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shema\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Deus é um</a>, a ideia de Deus como uma dualidade ou trindade entre os&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gentios\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Gentios\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">gentios</a>&nbsp;pode ser&nbsp;<i>shituf</i>&nbsp;(ou \"imperfeitamente&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monote%C3%ADsta\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Monoteísta\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">monoteísta</a>\"). Já o termo&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Ruach_HaKodesh&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ruach HaKodesh (página não existe)\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 88, 88); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ruach HaKodesh</a></i>&nbsp;(em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%C3%ADngua_hebraica\" title=\"Língua hebraica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">hebraico</a>:&nbsp;<span lang=\"he\" xml:lang=\"he\">??? ?????</span>&nbsp;-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Translitera%C3%A7%C3%A3o\" title=\"Transliteração\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">transl.</a>&nbsp;<i>ruah ha-qodesh</i>), \"Espírito Santo de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/YHWH\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"YHWH\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">YHWH</a>\", aparece frequentemente na no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talmud\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Talmud\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Talmud</a>&nbsp;e na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Midrash\" title=\"Midrash\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Midrash</a>, significando por vezes a inspiração profética e em outros é utilizado como uma&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hip%C3%B3stase\" title=\"Hipóstase\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">hipóstase</a>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meton%C3%ADmia\" title=\"Metonímia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">metonímia</a>&nbsp;de Deus<sup id=\"cite_ref-13\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-13\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[13]</a></sup>. O \"Espírito Santo\" rabínico tem um certo grau de personificação, mas permanece sendo uma \"qualidade de Deus, um de seus atributos\" e não, como na representação majoritária cristã, como sendo \"qualquer tipo de divisão metafísica da Divindade\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-14\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-14\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[14]</a></sup>. O&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Substantivo\" title=\"Substantivo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">substantivo</a>&nbsp;<i>ruach</i>&nbsp;(???, literalmente \"sopro\" ou \"vento\"), em várias combinações, aparece diversas outras vezes na Bíblia Hebraica, significando o \"espírito\" de Deus<sup id=\"cite_ref-15\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo#cite_note-15\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[15]</a></sup>.</p>', 0, 1),
