(9, 'Nossa Senhora da Conceição', '2013-12-08', 'SANTO_14022017120140_1.jpg', 'de 30 novembro a 08 de dezembr', '<div class=\"hatnote\" style=\"font-style: italic; padding-left: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><b>Nota:</b>&nbsp;Nossa Senhora da Conceição redireciona para este artigo. Para outros significados, veja&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nossa_Senhora_da_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o_(desambigua%C3%A7%C3%A3o)\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"Nossa Senhora da Conceição (desambiguação)\">Nossa Senhora da Conceição (desambiguação)</a>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imaculada_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o_(desambigua%C3%A7%C3%A3o)\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"Imaculada Conceição (desambiguação)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Imaculada Conceição (desambiguação)</a>.</div><table class=\"infobox_v2\" cellpadding=\"3\" border=\"0\" style=\"font-size: 12.32px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249); line-height: 1.1em; float: right; clear: right; margin: 0px 0px 0.5em 1em; width: 20em; border: 1px solid rgb(170, 170, 170); padding: 2px; font-family: sans-serif;\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"topo padrao\" style=\"vertical-align: middle; text-align: center; height: 45px; font-size: large; font-weight: bolder; line-height: 1.2em; background-color: gold;\"><span class=\"\">Nossa Senhora da Imaculada Conceição</span></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"center\" style=\"width: 250px;\"><div class=\"floatnone\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Murillo_immaculate_conception.jpg\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/61/Murillo_immaculate_conception.jpg/250px-Murillo_immaculate_conception.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/61/Murillo_immaculate_conception.jpg/375px-Murillo_immaculate_conception.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/61/Murillo_immaculate_conception.jpg/500px-Murillo_immaculate_conception.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"2012\" data-file-height=\"2952\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a></div></div><small>\"A Imaculada Conceição dos Veneráveis\", pintura de ~1678 de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bartolom%C3%A9_Esteban_Murillo\" title=\"Bartolomé Esteban Murillo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Bartolomé Esteban Murillo</a></small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: center;\">Nossa Senhora da Imaculada Conceição,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rainha\" title=\"Rainha\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Rainha</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Padroeira\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Padroeira\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Padroeira</a>&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portugal\" title=\"Portugal\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Portugal</a>, e de todos os&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lusofonia\" title=\"Lusofonia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Povos de Língua Portuguesa</a>&nbsp;(Exceto do Brasil, a qual a padroeira é Nossa Senhora Aparecida).</th></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; background-color: gold; font-weight: bold;\">Instituição da festa</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1476\" title=\"1476\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1476</a></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; background-color: gold; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/T%C3%ADtulos_de_Maria\" title=\"Títulos de Maria\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Venerada pela</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Cat%C3%B3lica\" title=\"Igreja Católica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Igreja Católica</a></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; background-color: gold; font-weight: bold;\">Principal&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_(edif%C3%ADcio)\" title=\"Igreja (edifício)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">igreja</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Santu%C3%A1rio_de_Nossa_Senhora_da_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o_de_Vila_Vi%C3%A7osa\" title=\"Santuário de Nossa Senhora da Conceição de Vila Viçosa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Santuário de Nossa Senhora da Conceição</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vila_Vi%C3%A7osa\" title=\"Vila Viçosa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Vila Viçosa</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portugal\" title=\"Portugal\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Portugal</a></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; background-color: gold; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lista_de_datas_comemorativas_de_Maria_(m%C3%A3e_de_Jesus)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lista de datas comemorativas de Maria (mãe de Jesus)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Festa litúrgica</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/8_de_Dezembro\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"8 de Dezembro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">8 de Dezembro</a></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; background-color: gold; font-weight: bold;\">Atribuições</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\">Concepção</td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; background-color: gold; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Padroeiro\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Padroeiro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Padroeira de</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portugal\" title=\"Portugal\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Portugal</a>&nbsp;e de toda a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lusofonia\" title=\"Lusofonia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Lusofonia</a>&nbsp;Exceto o Brasil, a qual a padroeira é Nossa Senhora Aparecida.</td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">A&nbsp;<b>Imaculada Conceição</b>&nbsp;é, segundo o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dogmas_da_Igreja_Cat%C3%B3lica\" title=\"Dogmas da Igreja Católica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">dogma católico</a>, a concepção da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virgem_Maria\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Virgem Maria\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Virgem Maria</a>&nbsp;sem mancha (em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Latim\" title=\"Latim\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">latim</a>,&nbsp;<i>macula</i>) do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pecado_original\" title=\"Pecado original\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">pecado original</a>. O dogma diz que, desde o primeiro instante de sua existência, a Virgem Maria foi preservada por&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deus\" title=\"Deus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Deus</a>&nbsp;da falta de graça santificante que aflige a humanidade, porque ela estava cheia de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gra%C3%A7a\" title=\"Graça\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">graça</a>&nbsp;divina. A Igreja Católica também professa que a Virgem Maria viveu uma vida completamente livre de pecado.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imaculada_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o#cite_note-1\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[1]</a></sup></p><div class=\"thumb tright\" style=\"clear: right; float: right; margin: 0.5em 0px 0.8em 1.4em; width: auto; border: none; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 252px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:0_L%27Immacul%C3%A9e_Conception_-_P.P._Rubens_-_Prado_-_P1627_-_(2).JPG\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d0/0_L%27Immacul%C3%A9e_Conception_-_P.P._Rubens_-_Prado_-_P1627_-_%282%29.JPG/250px-0_L%27Immacul%C3%A9e_Conception_-_P.P._Rubens_-_Prado_-_P1627_-_%282%29.JPG\" width=\"250\" height=\"364\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d0/0_L%27Immacul%C3%A9e_Conception_-_P.P._Rubens_-_Prado_-_P1627_-_%282%29.JPG/375px-0_L%27Immacul%C3%A9e_Conception_-_P.P._Rubens_-_Prado_-_P1627_-_%282%29.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d0/0_L%27Immacul%C3%A9e_Conception_-_P.P._Rubens_-_Prado_-_P1627_-_%282%29.JPG/500px-0_L%27Immacul%C3%A9e_Conception_-_P.P._Rubens_-_Prado_-_P1627_-_%282%29.JPG 2x\" data-file-width=\"1874\" data-file-height=\"2726\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:0_L%27Immacul%C3%A9e_Conception_-_P.P._Rubens_-_Prado_-_P1627_-_(2).JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Ampliar\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml%20version%3D%221.0%22%20encoding%3D%22UTF-8%22%20standalone%3D%22no%22%3F%3E%0A%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2011%2015%22%20width%3D%2215%22%20height%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cg%20id%3D%22magnify-clip%22%20fill%3D%22%23fff%22%20stroke%3D%22%23000%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22bigbox%22%20d%3D%22M1.509%201.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22smallbox%22%20d%3D%22M-1.499%206.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fg%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E%0A&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div><i>Imaculada Conceição</i>&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Paul_Rubens\" title=\"Peter Paul Rubens\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Peter Paul Rubens</a>&nbsp;no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Museu_do_Prado\" title=\"Museu do Prado\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Museu do Prado</a>.</div></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">A&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Festa\" title=\"Festa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">festa</a>&nbsp;da Imaculada Conceição, comemorada em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/8_de_dezembro\" title=\"8 de dezembro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">8 de dezembro</a>, foi definida como uma festa universal em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/28_de_Fevereiro\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"28 de Fevereiro\">28 de Fevereiro</a>&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1476\" title=\"1476\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1476</a>&nbsp;pelo&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papa_Sisto_IV\" title=\"Papa Sisto IV\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Papa Sisto IV</a>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">A Imaculada Conceição foi solenemente definida como dogma pelo&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papa_Pio_IX\" title=\"Papa Pio IX\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Papa Pio IX</a>&nbsp;em sua&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bula_papal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bula papal\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">bula</a>&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ineffabilis_Deus\" title=\"Ineffabilis Deus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ineffabilis Deus</a></i><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imaculada_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o#cite_note-2\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[2]</a></sup>&nbsp;em 8 de Dezembro de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1854\" title=\"1854\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1854</a>. A Igreja Católica considera que o dogma é apoiado pela&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/B%C3%ADblia\" title=\"Bíblia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Bíblia</a>&nbsp;(por exemplo, Maria sendo cumprimentada pelo&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anjo_Gabriel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Anjo Gabriel\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Anjo Gabriel</a>&nbsp;como \"<i>cheia de graça</i>\"), bem como pelos escritos dos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Padres_da_Igreja\" title=\"Padres da Igreja\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Padres da Igreja</a>, como&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Irineu_de_Lyon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Irineu de Lyon\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Irineu de Lyon</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ambr%C3%B3sio_de_Mil%C3%A3o\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ambrósio de Milão\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ambrósio de Milão</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imaculada_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o#cite_note-3\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[3]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imaculada_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o#cite_note-4\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[4]</a></sup>. Uma vez que Jesus tornou-se encarnado no ventre da Virgem Maria, era necessário que ela estivesse completamente livre de pecado para poder gerar seu Filho<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imaculada_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o#cite_note-5\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[5]</a></sup>.</p><h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 1em 0px 0.25em; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(162, 169, 177); font-size: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;Linux Libertine&quot;, Georgia, Times, serif; line-height: 1.3;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Fontes_b.C3.ADblicas\">Fontes bíblicas</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Imaculada_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: Fontes bíblicas\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Imaculada_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Editar secção: Fontes bíblicas\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar código-fonte</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">]</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Em sua&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Constitui%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Apost%C3%B3lica\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Constituição Apostólica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Constituição Apostólica</a>&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ineffabilis_Deus\" title=\"Ineffabilis Deus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ineffabilis Deus</a></i>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/8_de_dezembro\" title=\"8 de dezembro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">8 de dezembro</a>&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1854\" title=\"1854\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1854</a>), que definiu oficialmente a Imaculada Conceição como dogma, o Papa Pio IX recorreu principalmente para a afirmação de&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/G%C3%AAnesis\" title=\"Gênesis\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Gênesis</a>&nbsp;3:15</i>, onde Deus disse: \"<i>Eu Porei inimizade entre ti e a mulher, entre sua descendência e a dela</i>\", assim, segundo esta profecia, seria necessário uma mulher sem pecado, para dar à luz o Cristo, que reconciliaria o homem com Deus. O verso \"<i>Tu és toda formosa, meu amor, não há mancha em ti</i>\" (na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vulgata\" title=\"Vulgata\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Vulgata</a>: \"<i>Tota pulchra es, amica mea, et macula non est in te</i>\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imaculada_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o#cite_note-6\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[6]</a></sup>), no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/C%C3%A2ntico_dos_C%C3%A2nticos\" title=\"Cântico dos Cânticos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Cântico dos Cânticos</a>&nbsp;(4,7) é usado para defender a Imaculada Conceição, outros versos incluem:</p><blockquote style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\">\"Também farão uma arca de madeira&nbsp;<i>incorruptível</i>; o seu comprimento será de dois côvados e meio, e a sua largura de um côvado e meio, e de um côvado e meio a sua altura.\" (<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%8Axodo\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Êxodo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Êxodo</a>&nbsp;25:10-11</i>)</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">\"Pode o puro [Jesus] Vir dum ser impuro? Jamais!\"(Jó 14:4)</p><blockquote style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\">\"Assim, fiz uma arca de madeira&nbsp;<i>incorruptível</i>, e alisei duas tábuas de pedra, como as primeiras; e subi ao monte com as duas tábuas na minha mão.\" (<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deuteron%C3%B4mio\" title=\"Deuteronômio\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Deuteronômio</a>&nbsp;10:3</i>)</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Outras traduções para a palavras&nbsp;<i>incorruptível</i>&nbsp;(\"Setim\" em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%C3%ADngua_hebraica\" title=\"Língua hebraica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">hebraico</a>) incluem \"acácia\", \"indestrutível\" e \"duro\" para descrever a madeira utilizada.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/No%C3%A9\" title=\"Noé\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Noé</a>&nbsp;usou essa madeira porque era considerada muito durável e \"incorruptível\". Maria é considerada a Arca da Nova da Aliança (<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apocalipse\" title=\"Apocalipse\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Apocalipse</a>&nbsp;11:19</i>) e, portanto, a Nova Arca seria igualmente \"incorruptível\" ou \"imaculada\".</p><h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 1em 0px 0.25em; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(162, 169, 177); font-size: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;Linux Libertine&quot;, Georgia, Times, serif; line-height: 1.3;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Hist.C3.B3ria\">História</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Imaculada_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: História\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Imaculada_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Editar secção: História\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar código-fonte</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">]</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Desde o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cristianismo_primitivo\" title=\"Cristianismo primitivo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">cristianismo primitivo</a>&nbsp;diversos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Padres_da_Igreja\" title=\"Padres da Igreja\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Padres da Igreja</a>&nbsp;defenderam a Imaculada Conceição da Virgem Maria, tanto no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oriente\" title=\"Oriente\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Oriente</a>&nbsp;como no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ocidente\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ocidente\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ocidente</a>. No&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A9culo_IV\" title=\"Século IV\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">século IV</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Efr%C3%A9m_da_S%C3%ADria\" title=\"Efrém da Síria\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Efrém da Síria</a>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/306\" title=\"306\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">306</a>-<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/373\" title=\"373\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">373</a>),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Di%C3%A1cono\" title=\"Diácono\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">diácono</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Te%C3%B3logo\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Teólogo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">teólogo</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Compositor\" title=\"Compositor\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">compositor</a>&nbsp;de hinos, propunha que só&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jesus_Cristo\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Jesus Cristo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Jesus Cristo</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maria_(m%C3%A3e_de_Jesus)\" title=\"Maria (mãe de Jesus)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Maria</a>&nbsp;são limpos e puros de toda a mancha do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pecado\" title=\"Pecado\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">pecado</a>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Já no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A9culo_VIII\" title=\"Século VIII\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">século VIII</a>&nbsp;se celebrava a festa litúrgica da Conceição de Maria aos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/8_de_dezembro\" title=\"8 de dezembro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">8 de dezembro</a>&nbsp;ou nove meses antes da festa de sua natividade, comemorada no dia&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/8_de_setembro\" title=\"8 de setembro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">8 de setembro</a>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">No&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A9culo_X\" title=\"Século X\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">século X</a>, a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gr%C3%A3-Bretanha\" title=\"Grã-Bretanha\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Grã-Bretanha</a>&nbsp;celebrava a&nbsp;<i>Imaculada Conceição de Maria</i><span style=\"color: gray;\"><sup style=\"line-height: 1;\">[</sup></span><sup style=\"line-height: 1;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikip%C3%A9dia:Livro_de_estilo/Cite_as_fontes\" title=\"Wikipédia:Livro de estilo/Cite as fontes\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span title=\"Esta afirmação precisa de uma referência para confirmá-la.\"><span style=\"color: gray;\"><i>carece&nbsp;de fontes</i></span></span></a><span style=\"color: gray;\">]</span></sup>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">A festa da Imaculada Conceição de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/8_de_dezembro\" title=\"8 de dezembro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">8 de dezembro</a>&nbsp;foi definida em 28 de Fevereiro&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1476\" title=\"1476\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1476</a>&nbsp;pelo&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papa_Sisto_IV\" title=\"Papa Sisto IV\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Papa Sisto IV</a>. A existência da festa é um forte indício da crença da Igreja sobre a Imaculada Conceição mesmo antes da sua definição do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A9culo_XIX\" title=\"Século XIX\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">século XIX</a>&nbsp;como um dogma.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1497\" title=\"1497\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1497</a>, a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Universidade_de_Paris\" title=\"Universidade de Paris\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Universidade de Paris</a>&nbsp;decretou que ninguém poderia ser admitido na instituição se não defendesse a Imaculada Concepção de Maria, exemplo que foi seguido por outras universidades como a de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Universidade_de_Coimbra\" title=\"Universidade de Coimbra\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Coimbra</a>&nbsp;e de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Universidade_de_%C3%89vora\" title=\"Universidade de Évora\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Évora</a>. Em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1617\" title=\"1617\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1617</a>, o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papa_Paulo_V\" title=\"Papa Paulo V\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Papa Paulo V</a>&nbsp;proibiu que se afirmasse que Maria tivesse nascido com o pecado original, e em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1622\" title=\"1622\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1622</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Greg%C3%B3rio_V&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gregório V (página não existe)\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 88, 88); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Gregório V</a>&nbsp;impôs silêncio absoluto aos que se opunham à doutrina. Foi em 8 de Dezembro de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1661\" title=\"1661\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1661</a>&nbsp;que&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexandre_VII\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Alexandre VII\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Alexandre VII</a>&nbsp;promulgou a Constituição apostólica&nbsp;<i>Sollicitudo omnium Ecclesiarum</i>&nbsp;em que definia o sentido da palavra&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Conceptio&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Conceptio (página não existe)\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 88, 88); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">conceptio</a></i>, proibindo qualquer discussão sobre o assunto<sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imaculada_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o#cite_note-7\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[7]</a></sup>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/It%C3%A1lia\" title=\"Itália\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Itália</a>&nbsp;do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A9culo_XV\" title=\"Século XV\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">século XV</a>, o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ordem_dos_Frades_Menores\" title=\"Ordem dos Frades Menores\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">franciscano</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Bernardino_de_Bustis&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Bernardino de Bustis (página não existe)\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 88, 88); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Bernardino de Bustis</a>&nbsp;escreveu o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Of%C3%ADcio_da_Imaculada_Concei%C3%A7%C3%A3o\" title=\"Ofício da Imaculada Conceição\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ofício da Imaculada Conceição</a>, com aprovação oficial do texto pelo&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papa_Inoc%C3%AAncio_XI\" title=\"Papa Inocêncio XI\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Papa Inocêncio XI</a>&nbsp;em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1678\" title=\"1678\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1678</a>. Foi enriquecido pelo&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papa_Pio_IX\" title=\"Papa Pio IX\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Papa Pio IX</a>&nbsp;em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/31_de_mar%C3%A7o\" title=\"31 de março\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">31 de março</a>&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1876\" title=\"1876\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1876</a>, após a definição do dogma com 300 dias de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indulg%C3%AAncia\" title=\"Indulgência\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">indulgência</a>&nbsp;cada vez que recitado.</p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-weight: bold; margin: 0.3em 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6; font-family: sans-serif;\"><br></h3>', 1, 1);
INSERT INTO `padroeiro` (`padcodigo`, `padnome`, `paddata`, `padfoto`, `padperiodo`, `padhistorico`, `padampar`, `padappm`) VALUES
(10, 'Nossa Senhora das Dores', '2013-07-15', 'SANTO_14022017120211_1.jpg', 'de 09 a 15 de julho', '<p><b style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Nossa Senhora das Dores</b><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">, também chamada de&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Nossa Senhora da Piedade</b><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">,&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Nossa Senhora da Soledade</b><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">,&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Nossa Senhora das Angústias</b><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">,&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Nossa Senhora das Lágrimas</b><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">,&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Nossa Senhora das Sete Dores</b><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">,&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Nossa Senhora do Calvário</b><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">,&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Nossa Senhora do Monte Calvário</b><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">,&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Mãe Soberana</b><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;e&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Nossa Senhora do Pranto</b><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">, invocada em&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Latim\" title=\"Latim\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\">latim</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;como&nbsp;</span><i style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><b>Beata Maria Virgo Perdolens</b></i><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;ou&nbsp;</span><i style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><b>Mater Dolorosa</b></i><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;(sendo, sob essa designação, particularmente cultuada em&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portugal\" title=\"Portugal\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\">Portugal</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">), é uma forma pela qual é&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Venera%C3%A7%C3%A3o\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\" data-original-title=\"Veneração\">venerada</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maria_(m%C3%A3e_de_Jesus)\" title=\"Maria (mãe de Jesus)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\">Maria (mãe de Jesus)</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">.</span></p><h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 1em 0px 0.25em; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(162, 169, 177); font-size: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;Linux Libertine&quot;, Georgia, Times, serif; line-height: 1.3;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Venera.C3.A7.C3.A3o\">Veneração</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Nossa_Senhora_das_Dores&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: Veneração\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Nossa_Senhora_das_Dores&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Editar secção: Veneração\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar código-fonte</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">]</span></span></h2><div class=\"thumb tleft\" style=\"float: left; clear: left; margin: 0.5em 1.4em 0.8em 0px; width: auto; border: none; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 222px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Virgen_Pura_Dolorosa_de_Umbe.jpg\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4f/Virgen_Pura_Dolorosa_de_Umbe.jpg/220px-Virgen_Pura_Dolorosa_de_Umbe.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"284\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4f/Virgen_Pura_Dolorosa_de_Umbe.jpg/330px-Virgen_Pura_Dolorosa_de_Umbe.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4f/Virgen_Pura_Dolorosa_de_Umbe.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"373\" data-file-height=\"482\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Virgen_Pura_Dolorosa_de_Umbe.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Ampliar\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml%20version%3D%221.0%22%20encoding%3D%22UTF-8%22%20standalone%3D%22no%22%3F%3E%0A%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2011%2015%22%20width%3D%2215%22%20height%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cg%20id%3D%22magnify-clip%22%20fill%3D%22%23fff%22%20stroke%3D%22%23000%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22bigbox%22%20d%3D%22M1.509%201.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22smallbox%22%20d%3D%22M-1.499%206.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fg%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E%0A&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div>A Virgem Dolorosa aparecida em Umbe, perto&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bilbao\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bilbao\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Bilbao</a>, no Norte de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Espanha\" title=\"Espanha\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Espanha</a>.</div></div></div><div class=\"thumb tleft\" style=\"float: left; clear: left; margin: 0.5em 1.4em 0.8em 0px; width: auto; border: none; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 222px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Virgen_de_Chandavila.gif\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9d/Virgen_de_Chandavila.gif/220px-Virgen_de_Chandavila.gif\" width=\"220\" height=\"272\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9d/Virgen_de_Chandavila.gif/330px-Virgen_de_Chandavila.gif 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9d/Virgen_de_Chandavila.gif/440px-Virgen_de_Chandavila.gif 2x\" data-file-width=\"561\" data-file-height=\"694\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Virgen_de_Chandavila.gif\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Ampliar\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml%20version%3D%221.0%22%20encoding%3D%22UTF-8%22%20standalone%3D%22no%22%3F%3E%0A%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2011%2015%22%20width%3D%2215%22%20height%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cg%20id%3D%22magnify-clip%22%20fill%3D%22%23fff%22%20stroke%3D%22%23000%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22bigbox%22%20d%3D%22M1.509%201.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22smallbox%22%20d%3D%22M-1.499%206.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fg%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E%0A&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div>Nossa Senhora das Dores de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/La_Codosera\" title=\"La Codosera\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">La Codosera</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Espanha\" title=\"Espanha\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Espanha</a>.</div></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Em Heliodora/MG, é celebrado o Setenário das Dores de Maria, com 07 Santas Missas com a Temática das Sete Dores, começando no Quinto Domingo da Quaresma com a 1ª Dor e terminando no Sábado, véspera do Domingo de Ramos, com a 7ª Dor. No Sábado das Dores, realiza-se a Oração das 1000 Ave-Marias, divididas em 20 Santos Terços (05 Rosários), começando às 07 da manhã e caminhando o dia todo até às 19 horas, complementando a Celebração das 07 Dores de Nossa Senhora com a Santa Missa.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">É&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Orago\" title=\"Orago\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">padroeira</a>&nbsp;do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Munic%C3%ADpios_do_Brasil\" title=\"Municípios do Brasil\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">município</a>&nbsp;e da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diocese\" title=\"Diocese\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Diocese</a>&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guaxup%C3%A9\" title=\"Guaxupé\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Guaxupé</a>, em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minas_Gerais\" title=\"Minas Gerais\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Minas Gerais</a>. Também é padroeira das cidades de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Candiba\" title=\"Candiba\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Candiba</a>, no sudoeste da Bahia;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mairi\" title=\"Mairi\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mairi</a>, no centro-norte da Bahia;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Assar%C3%A9\" title=\"Assaré\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Assaré</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Corea%C3%BA\" title=\"Coreaú\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Coreaú</a>&nbsp;(como Nossa Senhora da Piedade), no Estado do Ceará;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Areal\" title=\"Areal\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Areal</a>&nbsp;no Estado do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_de_Janeiro\" title=\"Rio de Janeiro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Rio de Janeiro</a>;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Avar%C3%A9\" title=\"Avaré\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Avaré</a>, no interior de São Paulo; e também da capital do Estado do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Piau%C3%AD\" title=\"Piauí\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Piauí</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teresina\" title=\"Teresina\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Teresina</a>, onde é venerada no dia 15 de setembro, dia esse em que acontece uma celebração final com a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prociss%C3%A3o\" title=\"Procissão\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">procissão</a>&nbsp;que sai da Igreja Matriz de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nossa_Senhora_do_Amparo\" title=\"Nossa Senhora do Amparo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Nossa Senhora do Amparo</a>&nbsp;acompanhada por uma legião de pessoas que vão se formando à medida que a imagem vai passando pelas ruas do centro da cidade, até a sede da Catedral, onde é recebida por uma multidão de fiéis com chuvas de pétalas de rosas, folguetes e salvas de palmas, que simbolizam a fé e devoção pela Santa Padroeira.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Piren%C3%B3polis\" title=\"Pirenópolis\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Pirenópolis</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mag%C3%A9\" title=\"Magé\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Magé</a>, é venerada na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Semana_Santa\" title=\"Semana Santa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Semana Santa</a>, com o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Seten%C3%A1rio&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Setenário (página não existe)\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 88, 88); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Setenário</a>, e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prociss%C3%A3o\" title=\"Procissão\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">procissão</a>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Manten%C3%B3polis\" title=\"Mantenópolis\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mantenópolis</a>, é venerada no dia&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/15_de_setembro\" title=\"15 de setembro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">15 de setembro</a>, a festa começa no mês de agosto com a peregrinação com a imagem de Nossa Senhora das Dores pelas comunidades da Paróquia, iniciado pela comunidade&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Geraldo\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"São Geraldo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">São Geraldo</a>&nbsp;e indo até o município de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alto_Rio_Novo\" title=\"Alto Rio Novo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Alto Rio Novo</a>, que também faz parte da paróquia. Cada comunidade leva até a comunidade vizinha até o dia&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/15_de_setembro\" title=\"15 de setembro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">15 de setembro</a>, quando a imagem desce em Carreata desde o município de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alto_Rio_Novo\" title=\"Alto Rio Novo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Alto Rio Novo</a>&nbsp;até&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Manten%C3%B3polis\" title=\"Mantenópolis\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mantenópolis</a>, onde há uma&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Missa\" title=\"Missa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Missa</a>&nbsp;que é presidida pelo&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bispo\" title=\"Bispo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">bispo</a>&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Mateus\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"São Mateus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">São Mateus</a>&nbsp;finalizando a novena. Logo após à missa, há uma apresentação artística de cantores contratados pela paróquia.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boa_Esperan%C3%A7a_(Minas_Gerais)\" title=\"Boa Esperança (Minas Gerais)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Boa Esperança</a>, em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minas_Gerais\" title=\"Minas Gerais\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Minas Gerais</a>, é venerada na Semana Santa com o Setenário das Dores, e na semana do dia 15 de Setembro. Celebram-se&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Missa\" title=\"Missa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">missas</a>&nbsp;durante sete dias, até o dia de sua festa, quando, além de procissão por toda a cidade, celebram-se duas missas: uma de manhã, antes da procissão, e outra à noite. Ainda em Minas Gerais, Nossa Senhora da Soledade é festejada como a Padroeira da cidade de Itajubá, no sul do Estado, com realização de novena e festa religiosa sempre em torno da data de 15 de setembro. A celebração itajubense acontece principalmente na Paróquia Nossa Senhora da Soledade e é uma festa tradicional realizada em 2016 na sua 184ª edição ininterrupta.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Também é padroeira da cidade de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dores%C3%B3polis\" title=\"Doresópolis\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Doresópolis</a>, no Centro-Oeste de Minas Gerais e em Nossa Senhora das Dores, Sergipe.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Também em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maril%C3%A2ndia_do_Sul\" title=\"Marilândia do Sul\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Marilândia do Sul</a>, cidade do interior do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paran%C3%A1\" title=\"Paraná\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Paraná</a>, se tem, como fé religiosa, a devoção a Nossa Senhora das Dores, que originou o nome do município (Mari=Maria e lândia=terra), ou seja, Terra de Maria, em devoção à Santa. Após a posse do Padre José Natalício, na igreja matriz do município em 2008, é comemorada, no mês de setembro, a festa da paróquia em festejos em homenagem à santa. Como em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boa_Esperan%C3%A7a\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"Boa Esperança\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Boa Esperança</a>, em Minas Gerais, é celebrado um Setenário de missas, em homenagem às sete dores de Maria. Os festejos do mês de setembro da Paróquia Nossa Senhora das Dores de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maril%C3%A2ndia_do_Sul\" title=\"Marilândia do Sul\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Marilândia do Sul</a>&nbsp;vem conquistando cada vez mais o reconhecimento cultural regional, por sua organização através da fé, com boas festas, e leilões à tarde do domingo em que se comemora os festejos.</p><div class=\"thumb tright\" style=\"clear: right; float: right; margin: 0.5em 0px 0.8em 1.4em; width: auto; border: none; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 222px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Nossa_Senhora_das_Dores(Dores_de_Campos).jpg\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"Nossa Senhora das Dores em Dores de Campos, MG.\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Nossa_Senhora_das_Dores%28Dores_de_Campos%29.jpg/220px-Nossa_Senhora_das_Dores%28Dores_de_Campos%29.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"391\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Nossa_Senhora_das_Dores%28Dores_de_Campos%29.jpg/330px-Nossa_Senhora_das_Dores%28Dores_de_Campos%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Nossa_Senhora_das_Dores%28Dores_de_Campos%29.jpg/440px-Nossa_Senhora_das_Dores%28Dores_de_Campos%29.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"1836\" data-file-height=\"3264\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Nossa_Senhora_das_Dores(Dores_de_Campos).jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Ampliar\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml%20version%3D%221.0%22%20encoding%3D%22UTF-8%22%20standalone%3D%22no%22%3F%3E%0A%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2011%2015%22%20width%3D%2215%22%20height%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cg%20id%3D%22magnify-clip%22%20fill%3D%22%23fff%22%20stroke%3D%22%23000%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22bigbox%22%20d%3D%22M1.509%201.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22smallbox%22%20d%3D%22M-1.499%206.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fg%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E%0A&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div>A Senhora das Dores venerada em Dores de Campos<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nossa_Senhora_das_Dores#cite_note-1\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[1]</a></sup>, MG, cerca de 220 Km da capital estadual.</div></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">É a Santa Padroeira da cidade de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dores_de_Campos\" title=\"Dores de Campos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Dores de Campos</a>&nbsp;- MG, estando cerca de 220 Km da capital estadual.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">É Padroeira de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arthur_Nogueira\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Arthur Nogueira\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Arthur Nogueira</a>&nbsp;- SP, onde, no mês de setembro, se celebra o Setenário das Dores e, no dia 15 de setembro, a Missa Solene, seguida de Procissão pelas ruas do centro.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">É a Santa Padroeira da cidade de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miracatu\" title=\"Miracatu\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Miracatu</a>&nbsp;- SP.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">É a Santa Padroeira da cidade de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caldas_Novas\" title=\"Caldas Novas\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Caldas Novas</a>, em Goiás.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">É a Santa Padroeira da cidade de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Itobi\" title=\"Itobi\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Itobi</a>, em São Paulo.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">É a Santa Padroeira da cidade de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Casa_Branca\" title=\"Casa Branca\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Casa Branca</a>, em São Paulo.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">É a Santa Padroeira da cidade de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tubar%C3%A3o_(Santa_Catarina)\" title=\"Tubarão (Santa Catarina)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Tubarão (Santa Catarina)</a>, no sul de Santa Catarina, no Brasil, onde é feriado em 15 de setembro.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">É venerada no dia&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/15_de_Setembro\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"15 de Setembro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">15 de Setembro</a>, como padroeira da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eslov%C3%A1quia\" title=\"Eslováquia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Eslováquia</a>, do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Estados_dos_Estados_Unidos\" title=\"Estados dos Estados Unidos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">estado norte-americano</a>&nbsp;do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mississ%C3%ADpi\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mississípi\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mississípi</a>, dos municípios&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brasileiros\" title=\"Brasileiros\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">brasileiros</a>&nbsp;de Candiba Bahia,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mairi\" title=\"Mairi\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mairi</a>&nbsp;Bahia,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barbacena\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"Barbacena\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Barbacena</a>,<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dores_do_Turvo\" title=\"Dores do Turvo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Dores do Turvo</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Janu%C3%A1ria\" title=\"Januária\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Januária</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lima_Duarte\" title=\"Lima Duarte\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Lima Duarte</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Piedade_do_Rio_Grande\" title=\"Piedade do Rio Grande\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Piedade do Rio Grande</a>&nbsp;em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minas_Gerais\" title=\"Minas Gerais\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Minas Gerais</a>, estado onde em sua cidade de Itajubá, no sul, é a Padroeira como Nossa Senhora da Soledade; de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Areal\" title=\"Areal\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Areal</a>&nbsp;no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_de_Janeiro_(estado)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rio de Janeiro (estado)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Rio de Janeiro</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juazeiro_do_Norte\" title=\"Juazeiro do Norte\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Juazeiro do Norte</a>&nbsp;e Assaré,ambas no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cear%C3%A1\" title=\"Ceará\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ceará</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Avar%C3%A9\" title=\"Avaré\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Avaré</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brotas\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"Brotas\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Brotas</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ibi%C3%BAna\" title=\"Ibiúna\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ibiúna</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jambeiro_(S%C3%A3o_Paulo)\" title=\"Jambeiro (São Paulo)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Jambeiro (São Paulo)</a>, Serrana e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juquitiba\" title=\"Juquitiba\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Juquitiba</a>&nbsp;em São Paulo,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monteiro\" title=\"Monteiro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Monteiro</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mogeiro\" title=\"Mogeiro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mogeiro</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cajazeiras\" title=\"Cajazeiras\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Cajazeiras</a>, na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Para%C3%ADba\" title=\"Paraíba\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Paraíba</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caruaru\" title=\"Caruaru\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Caruaru</a>&nbsp;e Triunfo em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pernambuco\" title=\"Pernambuco\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Pernambuco</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Porto_Alegre\" title=\"Porto Alegre\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Porto Alegre</a>&nbsp;no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.w