(25, 'Nossa Senhora do Rosário', '2013-07-18', 'SANTO_14022017122603_1.jpg', '07 a 18 de julho', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><b>Nossa Senhora do Rosário</b>&nbsp;(ou&nbsp;<b>Nossa Senhora do Santo Rosário</b>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;<b>Nossa Senhora do Santíssimo Rosário</b>) é o título apresentado aquando da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apari%C3%A7%C3%B5es_marianas\" title=\"Aparições marianas\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">aparição da Santíssima Virgem Maria</a>&nbsp;a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Domingos_de_Gusm%C3%A3o\" title=\"Domingos de Gusmão\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">São Domingos de Gusmão</a>&nbsp;em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1208\" title=\"1208\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1208</a>&nbsp;na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mosteiro_de_Prouilhe\" title=\"Mosteiro de Prouilhe\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">igreja do mosteiro de Prouille</a>, na qual a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maria_(m%C3%A3e_de_Jesus)\" title=\"Maria (mãe de Jesus)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">mãe de Jesus</a>&nbsp;entregou o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Santo_Ros%C3%A1rio\" title=\"Santo Rosário\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Santo Rosário</a>&nbsp;ao frade dominicano.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Em agradecimento pela vitória da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Batalha_de_Muret\" title=\"Batalha de Muret\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Batalha de Muret</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sim%C3%A3o_IV_de_Monforte\" title=\"Simão IV de Monforte\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Simão IV de Monforte</a>&nbsp;construiu o primeiro santuário dedicado a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nossa_Senhora_da_Vit%C3%B3ria\" title=\"Nossa Senhora da Vitória\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Nossa Senhora da Vitória</a>. Em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1572\" title=\"1572\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1572</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papa_Pio_V\" title=\"Papa Pio V\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Papa Pio V</a>&nbsp;instituiu \"Nossa Senhora da Vitória\" como uma festa litúrgica para comemorar a vitória da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Batalha_de_Lepanto\" title=\"Batalha de Lepanto\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Batalha de Lepanto</a>. A vitória foi atribuída a Nossa Senhora por ter sido feita uma procissão do rosário naquele dia na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pra%C3%A7a_de_S%C3%A3o_Pedro\" title=\"Praça de São Pedro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Praça de São Pedro</a>, em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roma\" title=\"Roma\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Roma</a>, para o sucesso da missão da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liga_Santa_(Mediterr%C3%A2neo)\" title=\"Liga Santa (Mediterrâneo)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Liga Santa</a>&nbsp;contra os&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imp%C3%A9rio_Otomano\" title=\"Império Otomano\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">turcos otomanos</a>&nbsp;no oeste da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Europa\" title=\"Europa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Europa</a>. Em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1573\" title=\"1573\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1573</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papa_Greg%C3%B3rio_XIII\" title=\"Papa Gregório XIII\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Papa Gregório XIII</a>&nbsp;mudou o título da comemoração para \"Festa do Santo Rosário\" e esta festa foi estendida pelo&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Papa_Clemente_XII\" title=\"Papa Clemente XII\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Papa Clemente XII</a>&nbsp;à&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Cat%C3%B3lica\" title=\"Igreja Católica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Católica</a>. Após as reformas do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conc%C3%ADlio_Vaticano_Segundo\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Concílio Vaticano Segundo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Concílio Vaticano Segundo</a>&nbsp;a festa foi renomeada para Nossa Senhora do Rosário. A festa tem a classificação litúrgica de memória universal e é comemorada dia&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/7_de_outubro\" title=\"7 de outubro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">7 de outubro</a>, aniversário da batalha.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"></p><div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(162, 169, 177); background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); padding: 7px; font-size: 13.3px; display: table; zoom: 1; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><div id=\"toctitle\" style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: center;\"><h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: none; font-weight: bold; margin: 1em 0px 0.25em; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13.3px; display: inline; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.3;\">Índice</h2>&nbsp;<span class=\"toctoggle\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: 12.502px;\">&nbsp;[<a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"togglelink\" style=\"color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-