n: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Igreja do Rosário dos Pretos de Pirenópolis</a>, hoje no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_de_Nossa_Senhora_do_Carmo_(Piren%C3%B3polis)\" title=\"Igreja de Nossa Senhora do Carmo (Pirenópolis)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Museu de Arte Sacra do Carmo</a></div></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Nossa Senhora do Rosário também é, tradicionalmente, a santa de devoção dos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Negros\" title=\"Negros\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">negros</a>&nbsp;devido à semelhança entre o rosário e o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fio_de_contas\" title=\"Fio de contas\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">fio de contas</a>&nbsp;usado nas&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Religi%C3%B5es_de_matriz_africana\" title=\"Religiões de matriz africana\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">religiões de matriz africana</a>.</p><div class=\"thumb tleft\" style=\"float: left; clear: left; margin: 0.5em 1.4em 0.8em 0px; width: auto; border: none; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 302px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Igreja_Nossa_Senhora_do_Ros%C3%A1rio_-_Santa_Maria.JPG\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5e/Igreja_Nossa_Senhora_do_Ros%C3%A1rio_-_Santa_Maria.JPG/300px-Igreja_Nossa_Senhora_do_Ros%C3%A1rio_-_Santa_Maria.JPG\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5e/Igreja_Nossa_Senhora_do_Ros%C3%A1rio_-_Santa_Maria.JPG/450px-Igreja_Nossa_Senhora_do_Ros%C3%A1rio_-_Santa_Maria.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5e/Igreja_Nossa_Senhora_do_Ros%C3%A1rio_-_Santa_Maria.JPG/600px-Igreja_Nossa_Senhora_do_Ros%C3%A1rio_-_Santa_Maria.JPG 2x\" data-file-width=\"4288\" data-file-height=\"3216\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Igreja_Nossa_Senhora_do_Ros%C3%A1rio_-_Santa_Maria.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Ampliar\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml%20version%3D%221.0%22%20encoding%3D%22UTF-8%22%20standalone%3D%22no%22%3F%3E%0A%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2011%2015%22%20width%3D%2215%22%20height%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cg%20id%3D%22magnify-clip%22%20fill%3D%22%23fff%22%20stroke%3D%22%23000%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22bigbox%22%20d%3D%22M1.509%201.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22smallbox%22%20d%3D%22M-1.499%206.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fg%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E%0A&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div>Paróquia da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_de_Nossa_Senhora_do_Ros%C3%A1rio_(Santa_Maria)\" title=\"Igreja de Nossa Senhora do Rosário (Santa Maria)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Igreja de Nossa Senhora do Rosário</a>, fundada em 7 de outubro de 1959<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nossa_Senhora_do_Ros%C3%A1rio#cite_note-1\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[1]</a></sup>&nbsp;em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nossa_Senhora_do_Ros%C3%A1rio_(Santa_Maria)\" title=\"Nossa Senhora do Rosário (Santa Maria)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Nossa Senhora do Rosário</a>, em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Santa_Maria_(Rio_Grande_do_Sul)\" title=\"Santa Maria (Rio Grande do Sul)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Santa Maria</a>, no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Grande_do_Sul\" title=\"Rio Grande do Sul\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Rio Grande do Sul</a></div></div></div><h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 1em 0px 0.25em; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(162, 169, 177); font-size: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;Linux Libertine&quot;, Georgia, Times, serif; line-height: 1.3;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ver_tamb.C3.A9m\">Ver também</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Nossa_Senhora_do_Ros%C3%A1rio&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: Ver também\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); backgrou