(42, 'São Benedito', '2013-11-01', 'SANTO_23022017180850_3.jpg', 'de 24 de out a 01 de novembro', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><b>Benedito, o Mouro</b>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ordem_dos_Frades_Menores_Capuchinhos\" title=\"Ordem dos Frades Menores Capuchinhos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">OFM Cap</a>, conhecido também como&nbsp;<b>Benedito, o Negro</b>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;<b>Benedito, o Africano</b>, mas geralmente chamado simplesmente de&nbsp;<b>São Benedito</b>, é um&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Santo\" title=\"Santo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">santo</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cat%C3%B3licos\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Católicos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">católico</a>&nbsp;que, segundo algumas versões de sua história, nasceu na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sic%C3%ADlia\" title=\"Sicília\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Sicília</a>, sul da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/It%C3%A1lia\" title=\"Itália\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Itália</a>, em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1524\" title=\"1524\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1524</a>, no seio de família pobre e era descendente de escravos oriundos da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eti%C3%B3pia\" title=\"Etiópia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Etiópia</a>. Outras versões dizem que ele era um escravo capturado no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Norte_da_%C3%81frica\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Norte da África\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">norte da África</a>, o que era muito comum no sul da Itália nesta época. Neste caso, ele seria de origem&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mouro\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mouro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">moura</a>, e não&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eti%C3%B3pia\" title=\"Etiópia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">etíope</a>. De qualquer modo, todos contam que ele tinha o apelido de \"mouro\" pela cor de sua pele.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"></p><div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(162, 169, 177); background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); padding: 7px; font-size: 13.3px; display: table; zoom: 1; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><div id=\"toctitle\" style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: center;\"><h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: none; font-weight: bold; margin: 1em 0px 0.25em; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13.3px; display: inline; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.3;\">Índice</h2>&nbsp;<span class=\"toctoggle\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: 12.502px;\">&nbsp;[<a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"togglelink\" style=\"color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; cursor: pointer;\">esconder</a>]&nbsp;</span></div><ul style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0.3em 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-image: none;\"><li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benedito,_o_Mouro#Hist.C3.B3ria\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span class=\"tocnumber\" style=\"display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.5em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">1</span><span class=\"toctext\" style=\"display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit;\">História</span></a></li><li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benedito,_o_Mouro#Venera.C3.A7.C3.A3o\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span class=\"tocnumber\" style=\"display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.5em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">2</span><span class=\"toctext\" style=\"display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit;\">Veneração</span></a></li><li class=\"toclevel-1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benedito,_o_Mouro#Refer.C3.AAncias\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span class=\"tocnumber\" style=\"display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.5em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">3</span><span class=\"toctext\" style=\"display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit;\">Referências</span></a></li><li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benedito,_o_Mouro#Liga.C3.A7.C3.B5es_externas\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span class=\"tocnumber\" style=\"display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.5em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">4</span><span class=\"toctext\" style=\"display: table-cell; text-decoration: inherit;\">Ligações externas</span></a></li></ul></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"></p><h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 1em 0px 0.25em; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(162, 169, 177); font-size: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;Linux Libertine&quot;, Georgia, Times, serif; line-height: 1.3;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Hist.C3.B3ria\">História</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Benedito,_o_Mouro&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: História\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Benedito,_o_Mouro&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Editar secção: História\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar código-fonte</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">]</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Aos 18 anos de idade, já havia decidido consagrar-se ao serviço de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deus\" title=\"Deus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Deus</a>, e, aos 21, um monge dos irmãos eremitas de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Francisco_de_Assis\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"São Francisco de Assis\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">São Francisco de Assis</a>&nbsp;chamou-o para viver entre eles. Benedito aceitou. Fez&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Promessa\" title=\"Promessa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">votos</a>&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pobreza\" title=\"Pobreza\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">pobreza</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Obedi%C3%AAncia\" title=\"Obediência\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">obediência</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Castidade\" title=\"Castidade\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">castidade</a>, e, coerentemente, caminhava descalço pelas ruas e dormia no chão sem cobertas. Era muito procurado pelo povo, que desejava ouvir seus conselhos e pedir-lhe&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ora%C3%A7%C3%A3o\" title=\"Oração\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">orações</a>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Cumprindo seu voto de obediência, depois de 17 anos entre os eremitas, foi designado para ser cozinheiro no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Convento\" title=\"Convento\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Convento dos Capuchinhos</a>. Sua&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Piedade\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"Piedade\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">piedade</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sabedoria\" title=\"Sabedoria\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">sabedoria</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Santidade\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Santidade\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">santidade</a>&nbsp;levaram seus irmãos de comunidade a elegê-lo Superior do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mosteiro\" title=\"Mosteiro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mosteiro</a>, apesar de analfabeto e leigo, pois não havia sido ordenado sacerdote. Seus irmãos o consideravam iluminado pelo&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo\" title=\"Espírito Santo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Espírito Santo</a>, pois fazia muitas profecias. Ao terminar o tempo determinado como Superior, reassumiu com muita humildade mas com alegria suas atividades na cozinha do convento.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Sempre preocupado com os mais pobres do que ele, aqueles que não tinham nem o alimento diário, retirava alguns mantimentos do Convento, escondia-os dentro de suas roupas e os levava para os famintos que enchiam as ruelas das cidades. Conta a tradição que, em uma dessas saídas, o novo Superior do Convento o surpreendeu e perguntou-lhe: \" O que escondes aí, embaixo de teu manto, irmão Benedito?\" E o santo, humildemente, respondeu-lhe: \"<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rosa\" title=\"Rosa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Rosas</a>, meu senhor!\", e, abrindo o manto, de fato apareceram rosas de grande beleza e não os alimentos de que suspeitava o Superior.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">São Benedito morreu aos 65 anos, no dia&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/4_de_abril\" title=\"4 de abril\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">4 de abril</a>&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/1589\" title=\"1589\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">1589</a>, em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Palermo\" title=\"Palermo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Palermo</a>, na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/It%C3%A1lia\" title=\"Itália\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Itália</a>. Na porta de sua cela, no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Convento_de_Santa_Maria_de_Jesus_de_Palermo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Convento de Santa Maria de Jesus de Palermo (página não existe)\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 88, 88); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Convento de Santa Maria de Jesus de Palermo</a>, se encontra uma placa com a inscrição em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%C3%ADngua_italiana\" title=\"Língua italiana\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">italiano</a>&nbsp;indicando que era a Cela de São Benedito e, embaixo, as datas 1524-1589, para indicar as datas do nascimento e de sua morte. Alguns autores indicam 1526 como o ano de seu nascimento, mas os Frades do Convento de Santa Maria de Jesus consideram que a data certa é 1524.</p><div class=\"noprint\" style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif; clear: right; border: 1px solid rgb(170, 170, 170); margin: 0px 0px 1em 1em; font-size: 12.6px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249); width: 238px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; float: right;\"><div style=\"float: left; vertical-align: middle;\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Commons-logo.svg\" class=\"image\" title=\"Commons\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"Commons\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4a/Commons-logo.svg/22px-Commons-logo.svg.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"30\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4a/Commons-logo.svg/33px-Commons-logo.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4a/Commons-logo.svg/44px-Commons-logo.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"1024\" data-file-height=\"1376\"></a></div></div><div style=\"margin-left: 30px; line-height: normal; vertical-align: middle;\">O&nbsp;<a href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/P%C3%A1gina_principal\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"commons:Página principal\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Commons</a>&nbsp;possui imagens e outras mídias sobre&nbsp;<b><span class=\"plainlinks\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?title=Category%3ABenedict+the+Moor&amp;uselang=pt\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; padding: 0px !important;\">Benedito, o Mouro</a></span></b></div></div><h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: 1em 0px 0.25em; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(162, 169, 177); font-size: 1.5em; font-family: &quot;Linux Libertine&quot;, Georgia, Times, serif; line-height: 1.3;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Venera.C3.A7.C3.A3o\">Veneração</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Benedito,_o_Mouro&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: Veneração\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Benedito,_o_Mouro&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Editar secção: Veneração\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar código-fonte</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">]</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Todo ano a seguir à&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/P%C3%A1scoa\" title=\"Páscoa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Páscoa</a>, há uma&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Missa\" title=\"Missa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">missa</a>&nbsp;e festa em sua honra na localidade de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Coval&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Coval (página não existe)\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 88, 88); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Coval</a>, no concelho de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Santa_Comba_D%C3%A3o\" title=\"Santa Comba Dão\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Santa Comba Dão</a>, em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portugal\" title=\"Portugal\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Portugal</a>. Em Guaratinguetá, desde 1726, há cavalaria em louvor a São Benedito, tradicionalmente no domingo de Páscoa. No&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brasil\" title=\"Brasil\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Brasil</a>, o santo é tradicionalmente venerado pelos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Negros\" title=\"Negros\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">negros</a>, que relacionam o período de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Escravid%C3%A3o\" title=\"Escravidão\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">escravidão</a>&nbsp;e a origem africana do santo com o seu próprio passado de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Escravid%C3%A3o_no_Brasil\" title=\"Escravidão no Brasil\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">escravidão</a>&nbsp;e suas raízes africanas.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benedito,_o_Mouro#cite_note-1\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[1]</a></sup></p>', 1, 1),
