(49, 'São João ', '2013-06-24', 'SANTO_23022017180139_3.jpg', 'de 15 a 24 de junho', '<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"pt\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.25em; overflow: visible; padding: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(162, 169, 177); font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.3; font-family: &quot;Linux Libertine&quot;, Georgia, Times, serif;\">João, o Apóstolo</h1><div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\" style=\"position: relative; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 0.875em; z-index: 0; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><div id=\"siteSub\" style=\"display: inline; font-size: 12.88px;\">Origem: Wikipédia, a enciclopédia livre.</div><div id=\"contentSub\" style=\"font-size: 11.76px; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0px 0px 1.4em 1em; color: rgb(84, 84, 84); width: auto;\"></div><div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\" style=\"overflow: hidden; height: 0px; zoom: 1; user-select: none; margin-top: -1.4em; margin-bottom: 1.4em;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#mw-head\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"></a><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#p-search\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"></a></div><div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"pt\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\" style=\"direction: ltr;\"><div class=\"hatnote\" style=\"font-style: italic; padding-left: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><img alt=\"Disambig grey.svg\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4a/Disambig_grey.svg/20px-Disambig_grey.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"15\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4a/Disambig_grey.svg/30px-Disambig_grey.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4a/Disambig_grey.svg/40px-Disambig_grey.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"260\" data-file-height=\"200\">&nbsp;<b>Nota:</b>&nbsp;Ver também&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Evangelista\" title=\"João, o Evangelista\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">João, o Evangelista</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o_de_Patmos\" title=\"João de Patmos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">João de Patmos</a>&nbsp;para outras tradições ligadas a São João. Para outros significados, veja&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Jo%C3%A3o\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"São João\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">São João</a>.</div><table class=\"infobox_v2\" cellpadding=\"3\" border=\"0\" style=\"font-size: 12.32px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.1em; float: right; clear: right; margin: 0px 0px 0.5em 1em; width: 20em; border: 1px solid rgb(170, 170, 170); padding: 2px;\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"topo padrao\" style=\"vertical-align: middle; text-align: center; height: 45px; font-size: 14.784px; font-weight: bolder; line-height: 1.2em; background-color: gold;\"><span class=\"\">São João, o Apóstolo<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-1\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[1]</a></sup></span></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"center\" style=\"width: 300px;\"><div class=\"floatnone\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Le_Petit_Palais_-_Saint_Jean_l%27%C3%A9vang%C3%A9liste_-_16%C3%A8me_si%C3%A8cle_-_001.jpg\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/Le_Petit_Palais_-_Saint_Jean_l%27%C3%A9vang%C3%A9liste_-_16%C3%A8me_si%C3%A8cle_-_001.jpg/300px-Le_Petit_Palais_-_Saint_Jean_l%27%C3%A9vang%C3%A9liste_-_16%C3%A8me_si%C3%A8cle_-_001.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/Le_Petit_Palais_-_Saint_Jean_l%27%C3%A9vang%C3%A9liste_-_16%C3%A8me_si%C3%A8cle_-_001.jpg/450px-Le_Petit_Palais_-_Saint_Jean_l%27%C3%A9vang%C3%A9liste_-_16%C3%A8me_si%C3%A8cle_-_001.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/Le_Petit_Palais_-_Saint_Jean_l%27%C3%A9vang%C3%A9liste_-_16%C3%A8me_si%C3%A8cle_-_001.jpg/600px-Le_Petit_Palais_-_Saint_Jean_l%27%C3%A9vang%C3%A9liste_-_16%C3%A8me_si%C3%A8cle_-_001.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"3168\" data-file-height=\"4752\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a></div></div><small>Detalhe de uma&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pe%C3%A7a-de-altar\" title=\"Peça-de-altar\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">peça-de-altar</a>&nbsp;do século XVI com São João segurando um cálice envenenado (o veneno é simbolizado pelo dragão), uma das muitas tradições relacionadas a ele.</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: center; background-color: gold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ap%C3%B3stolo\" title=\"Apóstolo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Apóstolo</a></th></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; font-weight: bold;\">Nascimento</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Circa\" title=\"Circa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">ca.</a></i>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/6\" title=\"6\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">6</a>&nbsp;em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Betsaida\" title=\"Betsaida\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Betsaida</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Judeia_(prov%C3%ADncia_romana)\" title=\"Judeia (província romana)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Judeia</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imp%C3%A9rio_Romano\" title=\"Império Romano\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Império Romano</a></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; font-weight: bold;\">Morte</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Circa\" title=\"Circa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">ca.</a></i>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/100\" title=\"100\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">100</a>&nbsp;(94&nbsp;anos)&nbsp;em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%89feso\" title=\"Éfeso\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Éfeso</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%81sia_(prov%C3%ADncia_romana)\" title=\"Ásia (província romana)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ásia</a>, Império Romano</td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lista_de_santos\" title=\"Lista de santos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Veneração por</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Cat%C3%B3lica\" title=\"Igreja Católica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Igreja Católica</a><br><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Ortodoxa\" title=\"Igreja Ortodoxa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Igreja Ortodoxa</a></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Calend%C3%A1rio_hagiol%C3%B3gico\" title=\"Calendário hagiológico\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Festa litúrgica</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/27_de_dezembro\" title=\"27 de dezembro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">27 de dezembro</a>&nbsp;na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Cat%C3%B3lica\" title=\"Igreja Católica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Igreja Católica</a><br><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/26_de_setembro\" title=\"26 de setembro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">26 de setembro</a>&nbsp;na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Ortodoxa\" title=\"Igreja Ortodoxa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Igreja Ortodoxa</a></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simbologia_dos_santos\" title=\"Simbologia dos santos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Atribuições</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\">Livro; serpente num cálice; caldeirão; águia</td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrono\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Patrono\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Padroeiro</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\">Amor; lealdade; amizade; autores; livreiros; queimados; envenenados; comerciantes de obras de arte; editores; fabricantes de papel; escribas; acadêmicos; teólogos</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: center; background-color: gold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Gloriole.svg\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"Gloriole.svg\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Gloriole.svg/10px-Gloriole.svg.png\" width=\"10\" height=\"16\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Gloriole.svg/15px-Gloriole.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Gloriole.svg/20px-Gloriole.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"64\" data-file-height=\"105\"></a>&nbsp;<b><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portal:Santos\" title=\"Portal:Santos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Portal dos Santos</a></b></th></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\"><b>João, o Apóstolo</b>&nbsp;(em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aramaico\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"Aramaico\">aramaico</a>:&nbsp;<span lang=\"arc\" xml:lang=\"arc\">????? ?????</span>;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Translitera%C3%A7%C3%A3o\" title=\"Transliteração\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">transl</a>.:&nbsp;<span lang=\"arc-Latn\" title=\"ISO transliteration\" class=\"Unicode\" xml:lang=\"arc-Latn\" style=\"font-family: Code2000, Code2001, &quot;Free Serif&quot;, &quot;TITUS Cyberbit Basic&quot;, &quot;Doulos SIL&quot;, &quot;Chrysanthi Unicode&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Cyberbit&quot;, &quot;Bitstream CyberBase&quot;, Thryomanes, Gentium, GentiumAlt, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Free Sans&quot;, &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;;\"><i>Yohanan Shliha</i></span>; em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%C3%ADngua_hebraica\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"Língua hebraica\">hebraico</a>:&nbsp;<span lang=\"he\" xml:lang=\"he\">????? ?? ????</span>;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Translitera%C3%A7%C3%A3o\" title=\"Transliteração\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">transl</a>.:&nbsp;<span lang=\"he-Latn\" title=\"\" class=\"Unicode\" xml:lang=\"he-Latn\" style=\"font-family: Code2000, Code2001, &quot;Free Serif&quot;, &quot;TITUS Cyberbit Basic&quot;, &quot;Doulos SIL&quot;, &quot;Chrysanthi Unicode&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Cyberbit&quot;, &quot;Bitstream CyberBase&quot;, Thryomanes, Gentium, GentiumAlt, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Free Sans&quot;, &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;;\" data-original-title=\"ISO 259 Hebrew\"><i>Yohanan Ben Zavdai</i></span>;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Latim\" title=\"Latim\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">latim</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grego_koin%C3%A9\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Grego koiné\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">grego koiné</a>:&nbsp;<i>Ioannes</i>;&nbsp;<span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\"><i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Circa\" title=\"Circa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">ca.</a></i>&nbsp;6 d.C.&nbsp;–</span>&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Circa\" title=\"Circa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">ca.</a></i>&nbsp;100) foi um dos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doze_ap%C3%B3stolos\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Doze apóstolos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">doze apóstolos</a>&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jesus\" title=\"Jesus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Jesus</a>&nbsp;segundo o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Novo_Testamento\" title=\"Novo Testamento\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Novo Testamento</a>, filho de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zebedeu\" title=\"Zebedeu\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Zebedeu</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Salom%C3%A9_(disc%C3%ADpula)\" title=\"Salomé (discípula)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Salomé</a>&nbsp;e irmão de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tiago,_filho_de_Zebedeu\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tiago, filho de Zebedeu\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Tiago</a>, outro apóstolo. A tradição cristã acredita que ele teria sobrevivido aos demais apóstolos e teria sido o único a não sofrer o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/M%C3%A1rtir_crist%C3%A3o\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mártir cristão\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">martírio</a>. Os&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Padres_da_Igreja\" title=\"Padres da Igreja\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Padres da Igreja</a>&nbsp;consideram que ele era a mesma pessoa que&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o_Evangelista\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"João Evangelista\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">João Evangelista</a>&nbsp;(autor do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evangelho_de_Jo%C3%A3o\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"Evangelho de João\">Evangelho de João</a>),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o_de_Patmos\" title=\"João de Patmos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">João de Patmos</a>&nbsp;(autor do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apocalipse\" title=\"Apocalipse\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Apocalipse</a>) e o \"<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disc%C3%ADpulo_amado\" title=\"Discípulo amado\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">discípulo amado</a>\" citado por Jesus, uma crença seguida ainda hoje por diversas&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Denomina%C3%A7%C3%A3o_crist%C3%A3\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"Denominação cristã\">denominações cristãs</a>, incluindo a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Cat%C3%B3lica\" title=\"Igreja Católica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Igreja Católica</a>&nbsp;e a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Ortodoxa\" title=\"Igreja Ortodoxa\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Igreja Ortodoxa</a>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">A&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Santa_Tradi%C3%A7%C3%A3o\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Santa Tradição\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">tradição católica</a>&nbsp;afirma que João é o autor do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evangelho_de_Jo%C3%A3o\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Evangelho de João\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Evangelho de João</a>&nbsp;e de quatro outros livros do Novo Testamnto — as três&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Primeira_Ep%C3%ADstola_de_Jo%C3%A3o\" title=\"Primeira Epístola de João\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Epístolas de João</a>&nbsp;e o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apocalipse\" title=\"Apocalipse\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Apocalipse</a>. No Evangelho, a autoria é internamente creditada ao \"<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disc%C3%ADpulo_amado\" title=\"Discípulo amado\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">discípulo amado</a>\" (em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%C3%ADngua_grega_antiga\" title=\"Língua grega antiga\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">grego clássico</a>:&nbsp;<span lang=\"el\" class=\"politonico\" xml:lang=\"el\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Athena Unicode&quot;, Gentium, &quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;, &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Code2000;\">? ??????? ?? ????? ? ??????</span>;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Translitera%C3%A7%C3%A3o\" title=\"Transliteração\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">transl</a>.:&nbsp;<span lang=\"grc-Latn\" title=\"ISO 843 Greek\" class=\"Unicode\" xml:lang=\"grc-Latn\" style=\"font-family: Code2000, Code2001, &quot;Free Serif&quot;, &quot;TITUS Cyberbit Basic&quot;, &quot;Doulos SIL&quot;, &quot;Chrysanthi Unicode&quot;, &quot;Bitstream Cyberbit&quot;, &quot;Bitstream CyberBase&quot;, Thryomanes, Gentium, GentiumAlt, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Free Sans&quot;, &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;;\"><i>o math?t?s on ?gapa o I?sous</i></span>) em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Jo%C3%A3o/XX#20:2\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/João/XX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">João 20:2</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-2\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[2]</a></sup>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Jo%C3%A3o/XXI#21:24\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/João/XXI\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">João 21:24</a>&nbsp;afirma que o Evangelho de João é baseado no testemunho escrito do \"discípulo amado\". A autoria da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Literatura_joanina\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Literatura joanina\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">literatura joanina</a>&nbsp;tem sido debatida desde o ano 200<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-3\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[3]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-4\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[4]</a></sup>&nbsp;e sempre houve dúvidas se o houve de fato um indivíduo de nome \"João\" que escreveu todos estes livros. Seja como for, existe a noção de um \"João Evangelista\" e geralmente acredita-se que ele é o apóstolo João.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">Em sua \"<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hist%C3%B3ria_Eclesi%C3%A1stica_(Eus%C3%A9bio)\" title=\"História Eclesiástica (Eusébio)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">História Eclesiástica</a>\",&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eus%C3%A9bio_de_Cesareia\" title=\"Eusébio de Cesareia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Eusébio</a>&nbsp;afirma que a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Primeira_Ep%C3%ADstola_de_Jo%C3%A3o\" title=\"Primeira Epístola de João\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Primeira Epístola de João</a>&nbsp;e o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evangelho_de_Jo%C3%A3o\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Evangelho de João\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Evangelho de João</a>&nbsp;são amplamente creditados a ele. Porém, ele menciona que o consenso é que a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Segunda_Ep%C3%ADstola_de_Jo%C3%A3o\" title=\"Segunda Epístola de João\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">segunda</a>&nbsp;e a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Terceira_Ep%C3%ADstola_de_Jo%C3%A3o\" title=\"Terceira Epístola de João\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">terceira</a>&nbsp;epístolas de João não seriam dele e sim de um outro João. Além disso, ele se esforça para firmar ao leitor de que não um consenso geral sobre as \"revelações de João\", uma obra que, atualmente, acredita-se que só possa ser o \"Apocalipse\" (também chamado de \"Revelações\")<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-5\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[5]</a></sup>. O Evangelho de João é consideravelmente diferente dos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evangelhos_sin%C3%B3ticos\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Evangelhos sinóticos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">evangelhos sinóticos</a>, provavelmente escritos muito antes dele. Os bispos da Ásia Menor teriam supostamente pedido que João escrevesse seu evangelho para enfrentarem os&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ebionita\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ebionita\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">ebionitas</a>, que defendiam que&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pr%C3%A9-exist%C3%AAncia_de_Jesus\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pré-existência de Jesus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Cristo não teria existido</a>&nbsp;antes de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maria_(m%C3%A3e_de_Jesus)\" title=\"Maria (mãe de Jesus)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Maria</a>. João provavelmente conhecia e certamente aprovava os evangelhos de Mateus, Marcos e Lucas, mas estes relatavam a vida de Jesus focando primordialmente nos eventos posteriores à&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pris%C3%A3o_de_Jo%C3%A3o_Batista\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Prisão de João Batista\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">prisão</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Morte_de_Jo%C3%A3o_Batista\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Morte de João Batista\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">morte</a>&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o_Batista\" title=\"João Batista\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">João Batista</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-6\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[6]</a></sup>. Por volta de 600, porém,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sofr%C3%B4nio_de_Jerusal%C3%A9m\" title=\"Sofrônio de Jerusalém\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Sofrônio de Jerusalém</a>&nbsp;percebeu que&nbsp;<i>\"duas epístolas atribuídas a ele... são consideradas por alguns como sendo obra de um certo João, o Velho\"</i>&nbsp;e, depois de afirmar que o Apocalipse é obra de João de Patmos, ele teria sido&nbsp;<i>\"posteriormente traduzido por&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Justino_M%C3%A1rtir\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Justino Mártir\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Justino Mártir</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ireneu_de_Lyon\" title=\"Ireneu de Lyon\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ireneu</a>\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-Theophylact_7-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-Theophylact-7\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[7]</a></sup>, supostamente numa tentativa de reconciliar a tradição com as óbvias diferenças estilísticas no grego.</i></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">Até o século XIX, a autoria do Evangelho de João era universalmente atribuída ao apóstolo João. Porém, a maior parte dos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Biblista\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Biblista\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">biblistas</a>&nbsp;modernos tem dúvidas<sup id=\"cite_ref-John_8-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-John-8\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[8]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-foley_9-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-foley-9\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[9]</a></sup>. Alguns concordam em datar a obra em algum momento entre 65 e 85<sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-10\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[10]</a></sup>.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Arthur_Thomas_Robinson\" title=\"John Arthur Thomas Robinson\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">John Robinson</a>&nbsp;propõe uma primeira edição entre 50 e 55 e uma outra, final, em 65, com base em similaridades com os escritos de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paulo_de_Tarso\" title=\"Paulo de Tarso\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Paulo</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Robinson_11-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-Robinson-11\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[11]</a></sup><sup class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; margin-right: -3px;\"><span title=\"p. pp.284,307\" style=\"background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">:pp.284,307</span></sup>. Outros estudiosos afirmam que o Evangelho de João teria sido composto em dois ou até três estágios<sup id=\"cite_ref-12\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-12\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[12]</a></sup><sup class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; margin-right: -3px;\"><span title=\"p. p.43\" style=\"background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">:p.43</span></sup>. Há ainda os que defendem que ele não teria sido escrito até o terço final do século I, determinando a data mais antiga possível como algo entre 75 e 80<sup id=\"cite_ref-13\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-13\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[13]</a></sup>. Finalmente, há os que defendem uma data ainda mais tardia, talvez na última década do século I ou mesmo o início do século seguinte<sup id=\"cite_ref-14\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-14\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[14]</a></sup>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">Ainda assim, atualmente, muitos teólogos continuam a aceitar a autoria tradicional. Colin G. Kruse afirma que, como João Evangelista foi consistentemente citado nas obras dos primeiros Padres da Igreja,&nbsp;<i>\"é difícil ignorar esta conclusão, apesar da ampla relutância em aceitar [a autoria] por muitos, mas de forma alguma todos, os estudiosos modernos\"</i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Kruse_15-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-Kruse-15\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[15]</a></sup>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">A autoria anônima tem muitos defensores<sup id=\"cite_ref-sanders_16-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-sanders-16\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[16]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-ehrman_17-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-ehrman-17\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[17]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-lost_18-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-lost-18\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[18]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-19\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-19\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[19]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-20\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-20\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[20]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-21\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-21\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[21]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-22\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-22\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[22]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-23\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-23\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[23]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-24\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-24\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[24]</a></sup>. Segundo Paul N. Anderson, ele&nbsp;<i>\"contém mais reivindicações diretas de testemunho direto do que qualquer outra tradição evangélica\"</i><sup id=\"cite_ref-25\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-25\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[25]</a></sup>.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/F._F._Bruce\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"F. F. Bruce\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">F. F. Bruce</a>&nbsp;argumenta que&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Jo%C3%A3o/XIX#19:35\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/João/XIX\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">João 19:35</a>&nbsp;contém uma&nbsp;<i>\"enfática e explícita reivindicação de autoridade testemunhal direta\"</i><sup id=\"cite_ref-26\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-26\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[26]</a></sup>.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bart_D._Ehrman\" title=\"Bart D. Ehrman\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Bart D. Ehrman</a>, porém, não acredita que as reivindicações evangélicas tenham sido escritas por testemunhas diretas dos eventos relatados<sup id=\"cite_ref-lost_18-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-lost-18\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[18]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-27\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-27\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[27]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-iuda_28-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o,_o_Ap%C3%B3stolo#cite_note-iuda-28\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[28]</a></sup>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">Porém,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o_21\" title=\"João 21\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">João 21</a>&nbsp;termina (no versículo 24) com uma declaração explícita que unifica o autor (\"João Evangelista\") e a testemunha (\"João, o Apóstolo\"), na forma de um artifício literário de esconder ou adiar a descoberta do misterioso \"outro discípulo\", o \"discípulo amado\" e \"este homem\", as primeiras duas formas utilizadas múltiplas vezes durante o relato:</p><br></div></div>', 1, 1);
INSERT INTO `padroeiro` (`padcodigo`, `padnome`, `paddata`, `padfoto`, `padperiodo`, `padhistorico`, `padampar`, `padappm`) VALUES
(50, 'São José', '2013-03-29', 'SANTO_23022017182927_3.jpg', 'de 20 a 29 de marco', '<p><b style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">ão José</b><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;ou&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">José de Nazaré</b><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;ou&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">José, o Carpinteiro</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9#cite_note-1\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[1]</a></sup><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;foi, segundo o&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Novo_Testamento\" title=\"Novo Testamento\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\">Novo Testamento</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">, o esposo da&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maria_(m%C3%A3e_de_Jesus)\" title=\"Maria (mãe de Jesus)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\">Virgem Maria</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;e o pai adotivo de&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jesus\" title=\"Jesus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\">Jesus</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-mat.1.16_2-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9#cite_note-mat.1.16-2\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[2]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-luc.3.23_3-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9#cite_note-luc.3.23-3\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[3]</a></sup><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">. O nome José é a versão lusófona do&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hebraico\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hebraico\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\">hebraico</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><i style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Yosef</i><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;(????), por meio do&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Latim\" title=\"Latim\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\">latim</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><i style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Iosephus</i><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">. Descendente da casa real de&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/David\" title=\"David\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\">David</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">, é venerado como Santo pela&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Ortodoxa\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\" data-original-title=\"Igreja Ortodoxa\">Igreja Ortodoxa</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">,&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Anglicana\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\" data-original-title=\"Igreja Anglicana\">Igreja Anglicana</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">, e&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Cat%C3%B3lica\" title=\"Igreja Católica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\">Igreja Católica</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">, que o celebra como seu padroeiro universal. A&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liturgia\" title=\"Liturgia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\">Liturgia</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Luterana\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif;\" data-original-title=\"Igreja Luterana\">Luterana</a><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;também dedica um dia ? 19 de março ? à sua memória, sob o título de \"Tutor de Nosso Senhor\". Operário, é tido como \"Padroeiro dos Trabalhadores\", e, pela fidelidade a sua esposa e dedicação paternal a Jesus, como \"Padroeiro das Famílias\", emprestando seu nome a muitas igrejas e lugares ao redor do mundo.</span></p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-weight: bold; margin: 0.3em 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Escolha_como_noivo_a_Maria\">Escolha como noivo a Maria</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: Escolha como noivo a Maria\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Editar secção: Escolha como noivo a Maria\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar código-fonte</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">]</span></span></h3><div class=\"thumb tleft\" style=\"float: left; clear: left; margin: 0.5em 1.4em 0.8em 0px; width: auto; border: none; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 222px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Mar_Youssef.jpg\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ea/Mar_Youssef.jpg/220px-Mar_Youssef.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"365\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/ea/Mar_Youssef.jpg 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"316\" data-file-height=\"524\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Mar_Youssef.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Ampliar\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml%20version%3D%221.0%22%20encoding%3D%22UTF-8%22%20standalone%3D%22no%22%3F%3E%0A%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2011%2015%22%20width%3D%2215%22%20height%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cg%20id%3D%22magnify-clip%22%20fill%3D%22%23fff%22%20stroke%3D%22%23000%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22bigbox%22%20d%3D%22M1.509%201.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22smallbox%22%20d%3D%22M-1.499%206.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fg%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E%0A&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div>Imagem devocional popular de São José.</div></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Segundo um dos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Livros_ap%C3%B3crifos\" title=\"Livros apócrifos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Apócrifos</a>, José já em idade avançada teria sido reunido, pelo&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sumo_Sacerdote_de_Israel\" title=\"Sumo Sacerdote de Israel\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Sumo Sacerdote</a>, com os jovens de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jerusal%C3%A9m\" title=\"Jerusalém\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Jerusalém,</a>&nbsp;todos descendentes de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/David\" title=\"David\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Davi</a>, para saber qual deles seria o pai do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Messias\" title=\"Messias\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Messias</a>&nbsp;prometido. Cada um dos jovens tinha um cajado de madeira, e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deus\" title=\"Deus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Deus</a>&nbsp;responderia florindo o cajado do escolhido. O que teria acontecido com&nbsp;<strong class=\"selflink\">José</strong>, foi que cresceu um lírio em seu cajado. É uma bela tradição, mas a Igreja não tem como confirmá-la. O mais importante é que de fato&nbsp;<strong class=\"selflink\">São José</strong>, foi escolhido para ser o pai adotivo de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jesus\" title=\"Jesus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Jesus</a>.</p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-weight: bold; margin: 0.3em 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Paternidade\">A Paternidade</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: A Paternidade\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Editar secção: A Paternidade\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar código-fonte</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">]</span></span></h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Os&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evangelho\" title=\"Evangelho\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Evangelhos</a>&nbsp;e a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tradi%C3%A7%C3%A3o_cat%C3%B3lica\" title=\"Tradição católica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Sagrada Tradição Apostólica</a>&nbsp;afirmam que o verdadeiro genitor de Jesus é&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deus,_o_Pai\" title=\"Deus, o Pai\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Deus Pai</a>:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maria_(m%C3%A3e_de_Jesus)\" title=\"Maria (mãe de Jesus)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Maria</a>, já tendo sido prometida em casamento a José, concebeu&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milagre\" title=\"Milagre\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">miraculosamente</a>, sem que houvesse tido relações maritais com ninguém, por intermédio do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Esp%C3%ADrito_Santo\" title=\"Espírito Santo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Espírito Santo</a>. Para o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Casal\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"Casal\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">casal</a>, tratou-se de um momento&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drama\" title=\"Drama\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">dramático</a>, uma vez que, quando tomou ciência de que a esposa estava grávida de um filho que não era seu, José sentiu-se decepcionado e resolveu romper com ela, mas sem expô-la publicamente. O evangelista&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mateus_Evangelista\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mateus Evangelista\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mateus</a>&nbsp;assim relata o episódio:</p><table class=\"cquote2\" style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif; border-collapse: collapse; border-style: none;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(178, 183, 242); font-size: 40px; font-family: serif; font-weight: bold; padding: 10px;\">“</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 4px 10px;\"><i>«A origem de Jesus Cristo foi assim: Maria, sua mãe, comprometida em casamento com José, antes que coabitassem, achou-se grávida pelo Espírito Santo. José, seu esposo, sendo justo e não querendo denunciá-la publicamente, resolveu repudiá-la em segredo.»</i>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Mateus/I#1:18\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/Mateus/I\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mateus 1:18-19</a>)</td><td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: bottom; color: rgb(178, 183, 242); font-size: 40px; font-family: serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; padding: 10px;\">”</td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">No entanto, após uma experiência mística num sonho, no qual um&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anjo\" title=\"Anjo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Anjo</a>&nbsp;lhe aparecera, voltou atrás e reconheceu legalmente o Menino Jesus como seu legítimo filho.</p><table class=\"cquote2\" style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif; border-collapse: collapse; border-style: none;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(178, 183, 242); font-size: 40px; font-family: serif; font-weight: bold; padding: 10px;\">“</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 4px 10px;\"><i>«Eis que o Anjo do Senhor manifestou-se a ele em um sonho, dizendo: \'José, filho de Davi, não temas receber Maria, tua mulher, pois o que nela foi gerado vem do Espírito Santo. Ela dará à luz um filho e tu o chamarás com o nome de Jesus, pois ele salvará o seu povo dos seus pecados\'. (...) José, ao despertar do sono, agiu conforme o Anjo do Senhor lhe ordenara e recebeu em sua casa sua mulher.»</i>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Mateus/I#1:21\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/Mateus/I\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mateus 1:21-24</a>)</td><td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: bottom; color: rgb(178, 183, 242); font-size: 40px; font-family: serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; padding: 10px;\">”</td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Tendo assumido a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guarda\" title=\"Guarda\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">guarda</a>&nbsp;do menino, José ficou conhecido como suposto pai de Jesus<sup id=\"cite_ref-easton.joseph.4_4-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9#cite_note-easton.joseph.4-4\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[4]</a></sup>. O evangelista&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lucas_Evangelista\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lucas Evangelista\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Lucas</a>&nbsp;relata esse título:</p><table class=\"cquote2\" style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif; border-collapse: collapse; border-style: none;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(178, 183, 242); font-size: 40px; font-family: serif; font-weight: bold; padding: 10px;\">“</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 4px 10px;\"><i>«Ao iniciar&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minist%C3%A9rio_de_Jesus\" title=\"Ministério de Jesus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">seu ministério</a>, Jesus tinha mais ou menos trinta anos e era, conforme se supunha, filho de José.»</i>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Lucas/III#3:23\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/Lucas/III\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Lucas 3:23</a>)</td><td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: bottom; color: rgb(178, 183, 242); font-size: 40px; font-family: serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; padding: 10px;\">”</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-weight: bold; margin: 0.3em 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_profiss.C3.A3o\">A profissão</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: A profissão\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Editar secção: A profissão\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar código-fonte</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">]</span></span></h3><div class=\"thumb tleft\" style=\"float: left; clear: left; margin: 0.5em 1.4em 0.8em 0px; width: auto; border: none; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 172px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Georges_de_La_Tour._St._Joseph,_the_Carpenter.JPG\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/25/Georges_de_La_Tour._St._Joseph%2C_the_Carpenter.JPG/170px-Georges_de_La_Tour._St._Joseph%2C_the_Carpenter.JPG\" width=\"170\" height=\"235\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/25/Georges_de_La_Tour._St._Joseph%2C_the_Carpenter.JPG/255px-Georges_de_La_Tour._St._Joseph%2C_the_Carpenter.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/25/Georges_de_La_Tour._St._Joseph%2C_the_Carpenter.JPG/340px-Georges_de_La_Tour._St._Joseph%2C_the_Carpenter.JPG 2x\" data-file-width=\"2024\" data-file-height=\"2794\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Georges_de_La_Tour._St._Joseph,_the_Carpenter.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Ampliar\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml%20version%3D%221.0%22%20encoding%3D%22UTF-8%22%20standalone%3D%22no%22%3F%3E%0A%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2011%2015%22%20width%3D%2215%22%20height%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cg%20id%3D%22magnify-clip%22%20fill%3D%22%23fff%22%20stroke%3D%22%23000%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22bigbox%22%20d%3D%22M1.509%201.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22smallbox%22%20d%3D%22M-1.499%206.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fg%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E%0A&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div><i>São José, o Carpinteiro</i>, de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Georges_de_La_Tour\" title=\"Georges de La Tour\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Georges de La Tour</a>, 1640.</div></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">A profissão de José é mencionada pelo&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mateus_(evangelista)\" title=\"Mateus (evangelista)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">evangelista Mateus</a>&nbsp;quando afirma, no capítulo 13 e versículo 55 de seu Evangelho, que&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jesus\" title=\"Jesus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Jesus</a>&nbsp;era filho de um&nbsp;<i>tekt?n</i>&nbsp;(??????): termo grego que costuma receber várias interpretações. Ainda que a tradição lhe atribua estritamente a profissão de carpinteiro, o fato é que o título grego é genérico, sendo usado para designar os trabalhadores envolvidos em atividades econômicas ligadas à construção civil. Outras vertentes costumam considerar José como sendo um&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Canteiro\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Canteiro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">canteiro</a>, ou seja, um operário que talhava artisticamente blocos de rocha bruta.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Os evangelhos reivindicam que Jesus, antes de iniciar&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vida_p%C3%BAblica_de_Jesus\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vida pública de Jesus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">sua vida pública</a>, desempenhou a profissão do pai. O primeiro evangelista que atribui-lhe o título é&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Marcos\" title=\"São Marcos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">São Marcos</a>, que refere-se a Jesus como \"o Carpinteiro\", no capítulo VI, versículo 3 da sua narrativa sinótica que relata uma sua visita a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nazar%C3%A9\" title=\"Nazaré\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Nazaré</a>&nbsp;na qual seus compatriotas chamavam-no ironicamente pela profissão para desqualificá-lo como pregador. Mateus, por sua vez, retoma o mesmo episódio na sua versão do evangelho, mas com uma variante:</p><table class=\"cquote2\" style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif; border-collapse: collapse; border-style: none;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(178, 183, 242); font-size: 40px; font-family: serif; font-weight: bold; padding: 10px;\">“</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 4px 10px;\"><i>«Não é o filho do carpinteiro? Não se chama a mãe dele Maria e os seus irmãos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tiago_(irm%C3%A3o_de_Jesus)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tiago (irmão de Jesus)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Tiago</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Jos%C3%A9_(irm%C3%A3o_de_Jesus)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"José (irmão de Jesus) (página não existe)\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 88, 88); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">José</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Judas_(irm%C3%A3o_de_Jesus)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Judas (irmão de Jesus)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Judas</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sim%C3%A3o_(irm%C3%A3o_de_Jesus)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Simão (irmão de Jesus)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Simão</a>?»</i>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Mateus/XIII#13:55\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/Mateus/XIII\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mateus 13:55</a>)</td><td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: bottom; color: rgb(178, 183, 242); font-size: 40px; font-family: serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; padding: 10px;\">”</td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">A tradicional tradução da expressão grega&nbsp;<i>tekt?n</i>&nbsp;por&nbsp;<i>carpinteiro</i>&nbsp;se deve ao fato de que os&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Padres_da_Igreja\" title=\"Padres da Igreja\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Padres da Igreja</a>&nbsp;e a própria&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vulgata\" title=\"Vulgata\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Vulgata</a>&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jer%C3%B3nimo_de_Estrid%C3%A3o\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Jerónimo de Estridão\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">São Jerônimo</a>&nbsp;versavam-na para o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caso_nominativo\" title=\"Caso nominativo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">nominativo</a>&nbsp;latino&nbsp;<i>f?b?r, fabri</i>: termo que denota o artesão.</p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-weight: bold; margin: 0.3em 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_genealogia_de_Jos.C3.A9\">A genealogia de José</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: A genealogia de José\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Editar secção: A genealogia de José\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar código-fonte</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">]</span></span></h3><div class=\"hatnote\" style=\"font-style: italic; padding-left: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Magnifying_glass_01.svg/17px-Magnifying_glass_01.svg.png\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Magnifying_glass_01.svg/26px-Magnifying_glass_01.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Magnifying_glass_01.svg/34px-Magnifying_glass_01.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"663\" data-file-height=\"659\">Ver artigo principal:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Genealogia_de_Jesus\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"Genealogia de Jesus\">Genealogia de Jesus</a></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">As notícias dos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evangelhos_sin%C3%B3pticos\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"Evangelhos sinópticos\">evangelhos sinóticos</a>&nbsp;sobre São José são escassíssimas. Lucas e Mateus narram episódios cristocêntricos em que o carpinteiro está envolvido, dizendo que José era descendente do rei Davi e residia no pequeno povoado de Nazaré; João apenas o menciona como membro da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sagrada_Fam%C3%ADlia\" title=\"Sagrada Família\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Sagrada Família</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-mt.6.11_5-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9#cite_note-mt.6.11-5\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[5]</a></sup>; ao passo que Marcos sequer cita expressamente seu nome.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">As versões dos dois evangelistas que pormenorizam a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%81rvore_geneal%C3%B3gica\" title=\"Árvore genealógica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">árvore genealógica</a>&nbsp;de Jesus divergem no que se refere a quem teria sido o pai de José:</p><table class=\"cquote2\" style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif; border-collapse: collapse; border-style: none;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(178, 183, 242); font-size: 40px; font-family: serif; font-weight: bold; padding: 10px;\">“</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 4px 10px;\"><i>«<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jac%C3%B3\" title=\"Jacó\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Jacó</a>&nbsp;gerou José, o esposo de Maria da qual nasceu Jesus chamado Cristo.»</i>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Mateus/I#1:16\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/Mateus/I\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mateus 1:16</a>)</td><td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: bottom; color: rgb(178, 183, 242); font-size: 40px; font-family: serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; padding: 10px;\">”</td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"cquote2\" style=\"color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif; border-collapse: collapse; border-style: none;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(178, 183, 242); font-size: 40px; font-family: serif; font-weight: bold; padding: 10px;\">“</td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; padding: 4px 10px;\"><i>«Ao iniciar seu ministério, Jesus tinha mais ou menos trinta anos e era, conforme se supunha, filho de José, filho de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eli\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"Eli\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Eli</a>.»</i>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Lucas/III#3:23\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/Lucas/III\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Lucas 3:23</a>)</td><td style=\"width: 20px; vertical-align: bottom; color: rgb(178, 183, 242); font-size: 40px; font-family: serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; padding: 10px;\">”</td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">A teologia&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Protestantismo\" title=\"Protestantismo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">protestante</a>&nbsp;tenta elucidar essa discrepância, afirmando que&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Lucas\" title=\"São Lucas\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Lucas</a>, na verdade, estivesse registrando a genealogia de Maria, ao passo que&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mateus_(evangelista)\" title=\"Mateus (evangelista)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Mateus</a>, esse sim, a de José<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9#cite_note-6\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[6]</a></sup>. Segundo esta vertente, Mateus segue a linhagem de José segundo a lei, remontando a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Salom%C3%A3o\" title=\"Salomão\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Salomão</a>, filho de Davi; Lucas, por sua vez, estaria seguindo a linhagem consanguínea de Jesus, por meio de Maria, esposa de José, mencionando&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nat%C3%A3\" title=\"Natã\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Natã</a>, filho de Davi. Como não havia designação própria para&nbsp;<i>genro</i><sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9#cite_note-7\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[7]</a></sup>, José teria sido considerado um filho de Eli por ter se casado com Maria, filha de Eli. A interpretação é compartilhada pela Igreja Católica, cuja tradição considera ser Eli (<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eliaquim\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"Eliaquim\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Eliaquim</a>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joaquim\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"Joaquim\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Joaquim</a>) o pai de Maria<sup id=\"cite_ref-catholic.genealogy.of.christ_8-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/S%C3%A3o_Jos%C3%A9#cite_note-catholic.genealogy.of.christ-8\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[8]</a></sup>.</p><div class=\"thumb tright\" style=\"clear: right; float: right; margin: 0.5em 0px 0.8em 1.4em; width: auto; border: none; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 222px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Genealogy_of_Jesus_mosaic_at_Chora_(1).jpg\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/62/Genealogy_of_Jesus_mosaic_at_Chora_%281%29.jpg/220px-Genealogy_of_Jesus_mosaic_at_Chora_%281%29.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"147\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/62/Genealogy_of_Jesus_mosaic_at_Chora_%281%29.jpg/330px-Genealogy_of_Jesus_mosaic_at_Chora_%281%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/62/Genealogy_of_Jesus_mosaic_at_Chora_%281%29.jpg/440px-Genealogy_of_Jesus_mosaic_at_Chora_%281%29.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"3456\" data-file-height=\"2304\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Genealogy_of_Jesus_mosaic_at_Chora_(1).jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Ampliar\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml%20version%3D%221.0%22%20encoding%3D%22UTF-8%22%20standalone%3D%22no%22%3F%3E%0A%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2011%2015%22%20width%3D%2215%22%20height%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cg%20id%3D%22magnify-clip%22%20fill%3D%22%23fff%22%20stroke%3D%22%23000%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22bigbox%22%20d%3D%22M1.509%201.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22smallbox%22%20d%3D%22M-1.499%206.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fg%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E%0A&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div>Mosaico na cúpula sul da Igreja de São Salvador em Chora de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Istambul\" title=\"Istambul\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Istambul</a>, agregando os alegados filhos de S. José à genealogia de Cristo&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pantocrator\" title=\"Pantocrator\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Pantocrator</a>.</div></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); font-family: sans-serif;\">Se por um lado os evangelhos canônicos são reticentes em relação ao carpinteiro de Nazaré, os apócrifos oferecem detalhes interessantes, especialmente o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Protoevangelho_de_Tiago\" title=\"Protoevangelho de Tiago\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Protoevangelho de Tiago</a>, escrito provavelmente no ano de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/150\" title=\"150\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">150</a>&nbsp;que afirma que José era originário de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bel%C3%A9m_(Palestina)\" title=\"Belém (Palestina)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Belém</a>&nbsp;e, antes do matrimônio com a Virgem Maria, teria se casado com uma mulher com quem teve seis filhos: quatro homens (Judas, José, Tiago e Simão) e duas mulheres (Lísia e Lídia). No entanto, teria ficado viúvo bem cedo e com os filhos para educar. A Igreja Ortodoxa acolhe esta versão, retratada nos mosaicos da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_de_S%C3%A3o_Salvador_em_Chora\" title=\"Igreja de São Salvador em Chora\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Igreja de São Salvador em Chora</a>&nbsp;de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Constantinopla\" title=\"Constantinopla\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Constantinopla</a>, ainda que a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Cat%C3%B3lica\" title=\"Igreja Católica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Igreja Católica</a>&nbsp;rejeite essa tradição.</p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-weight: bold; margin: 0.3em 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6; font-family: sans-serif;\"><br></h3>', 1, 1);
