=\"topo padrao\" style=\"vertical-align: middle; text-align: center; height: 45px; font-size: 14.784px; font-weight: bolder; line-height: 1.2em; background-color: gold;\"><span class=\"\">São Miguel Arcanjo</span></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"center\" style=\"width: 230px;\"><div class=\"floatnone\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Guido_Reni_031.jpg\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Guido_Reni_031.jpg/200px-Guido_Reni_031.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"299\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Guido_Reni_031.jpg/300px-Guido_Reni_031.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Guido_Reni_031.jpg/400px-Guido_Reni_031.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"1576\" data-file-height=\"2358\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></a></div></div><small>Arcanjo Miguel (por&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guido_Reni\" title=\"Guido Reni\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Guido Reni</a>).</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: center; background-color: gold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arcanjo\" title=\"Arcanjo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Arcanjo</a>&nbsp;e \"Príncipe da Milícia Celeste\"</th></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lista_de_santos\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"Lista de santos\">Veneração por</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cristianismo\" title=\"Cristianismo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Cristandade</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juda%C3%ADsmo\" title=\"Judaísmo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Judaísmo</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isl%C3%A3o\" title=\"Islão\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Islamismo</a></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Calend%C3%A1rio_hagiol%C3%B3gico\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"Calendário hagiológico\">Festa litúrgica</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/29_de_setembro\" title=\"29 de setembro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">29 de setembro</a></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simbologia_dos_santos\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"Simbologia dos santos\">Atribuições</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Escudo\" title=\"Escudo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Escudo</a>&nbsp;(\"Quis ut Deus\"); Lutando contra o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drag%C3%A3o\" title=\"Dragão\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Dragão</a>; segurando a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Balan%C3%A7a\" title=\"Balança\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">balança</a>, como o juiz dos mortos</td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" style=\"vertical-align: top; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrono\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Patrono\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Padroeiro</a></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top;\">dos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fuzileiros_navais\" title=\"Fuzileiros navais\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">fuzileiros navais</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marinheiro\" title=\"Marinheiro\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">marinheiros</a>, motoristas de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ambul%C3%A2ncia\" title=\"Ambulância\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">ambulância</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Param%C3%A9dico\" title=\"Paramédico\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">paramédicos</a>, policiais,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paraquedismo\" title=\"Paraquedismo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">paraquedistas</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Radiologia\" title=\"Radiologia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">radiologistas</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Radioterapia\" title=\"Radioterapia\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">radioterapeutas</a>&nbsp;e da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Igreja_Cat%C3%B3lica\" title=\"Igreja Católica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Santa Igreja Católica Apostólica Romana</a>; das cidades de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bruxelas\" title=\"Bruxelas\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Bruxelas</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kiev\" title=\"Kiev\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Kiev</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arcangel\" title=\"Arcangel\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Arcangel</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Santos_Dumont\" title=\"Santos Dumont\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Santos Dumont</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align: top; text-align: center; background-color: gold;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Gloriole.svg\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"Gloriole.svg\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Gloriole.svg/10px-Gloriole.svg.png\" width=\"10\" height=\"16\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Gloriole.svg/15px-Gloriole.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Gloriole.svg/20px-Gloriole.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"64\" data-file-height=\"105\"></a>&nbsp;<b><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portal:Santos\" title=\"Portal:Santos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Portal dos Santos</a></b></th></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\"><b>Miguel</b>&nbsp;(em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%C3%ADngua_hebraica\" title=\"Língua hebraica\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">hebraico</a>:&nbsp;<span lang=\"he\" xml:lang=\"he\">????????</span>&nbsp;(<i>Micha\'el</i>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;<i>Mîkh?\'?l</i>; em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%C3%ADngua_grega\" title=\"Língua grega\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">grego</a>:&nbsp;<span lang=\"el\" class=\"politonico\" xml:lang=\"el\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Athena Unicode&quot;, Gentium, &quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;, &quot;Arial Unicode MS&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Code2000;\">??????</span>,&nbsp;<i>Mikha?l</i>; em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Latim\" title=\"Latim\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">latim</a>:&nbsp;<span lang=\"la\" xml:lang=\"la\">Michael</span>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;<i>Míchaël</i>; em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%C3%ADngua_%C3%A1rabe\" title=\"Língua árabe\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">árabe</a>:&nbsp;<span lang=\"ar\" xml:lang=\"ar\">???????</span>,&nbsp;<i>M?kh?\'?l</i>) é um&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arcanjo\" title=\"Arcanjo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">arcanjo</a>&nbsp;nas doutrinas religiosas&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Judaicas\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Judaicas\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">judaicas</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crist%C3%A3s\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Cristãs\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">cristãs</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isl%C3%A2micas\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Islâmicas\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">islâmicas</a>. Os&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cat%C3%B3licos\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Católicos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">católicos</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anglicanos\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Anglicanos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">anglicanos</a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Luteranos\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Luteranos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">luteranos</a>&nbsp;se referem a ele como&nbsp;<b>São Miguel Arcanjo</b>&nbsp;ou simplesmente como&nbsp;<b>São Miguel</b>. Os&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ortodoxos\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ortodoxos\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">ortodoxos</a>&nbsp;se referem a ele como&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Texiarca&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Texiarca (página não existe)\" style=\"color: rgb(165, 88, 88); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Texiarca</a>&nbsp;Arcanjo Miguel</i>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: gray;\"><sup style=\"line-height: 1;\">[</sup></span><sup style=\"line-height: 1;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikip%C3%A9dia:Livro_de_estilo/Cite_as_fontes\" title=\"Wikipédia:Livro de estilo/Cite as fontes\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span title=\"Esta afirmação precisa de uma referência para confirmá-la.\"><span style=\"color: gray;\"><i>carece&nbsp;de fontes</i></span></span></a><span style=\"color: gray;\">]</span></sup>&nbsp;ou simplesmente como&nbsp;<b>Arcanjo Miguel</b>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\">Em hebraico,&nbsp;<i>Miguel</i>&nbsp;significa \"aquele que é similar a Deus\" (<i>mi</i>-\"quem\",&nbsp;<i>ka</i>-\"como\",&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/El_(deus)\" title=\"El (deus)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">El</a></i>-\"deus\"), o que é tradicionalmente interpretado como uma pergunta retórica: \"<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#Do_termo_.E2.80.9CMiguel.E2.80.9D\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" data-original-title=\"Miguel (arcanjo)\">Quem como Deus?</a>\" (em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Latim\" title=\"Latim\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">latim</a>:&nbsp;<span lang=\"la\" xml:lang=\"la\"><i>Quis ut Deus?</i></span>), para a qual se espera uma resposta negativa, e que implica que \"ninguém\" é como&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deus\" title=\"Deus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Deus</a>. Assim, Miguel é reinterpretado como um símbolo de humildade perante Deus<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-1\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[1]</a></sup>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\">Na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tanakh\" title=\"Tanakh\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Bíblia Hebraica</a>, Miguel é mencionado três vezes no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Livro_de_Daniel\" title=\"Livro de Daniel\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Livro de Daniel</a>, uma como um \"grande príncipe que defende as crianças do seu povo\". A ideia de Miguel como um advogado de defesa dos&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Judeus\" title=\"Judeus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">judeus</a>&nbsp;se tornou tão prevalente que, a despeito da proibição rabínica contra se apelar aos anjos como intermediários entre Deus e seu povo, Miguel acabou tomando um lugar importante na liturgia judaica.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\">Em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikisource.org/wiki/Tradu%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_da_B%C3%ADblia/Apocalipse/XII#12:7\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"s:Tradução Brasileira da Bíblia/Apocalipse/XII\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Apocalipse 12:7-9</a>, Miguel lidera os exércitos de Deus contra as forças de&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sat%C3%A3\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Satã\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Satã</a>&nbsp;e seus anjos e os derrota durante a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Armagedom\" title=\"Armagedom\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">guerra no céu</a>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\">Na&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ep%C3%ADstola_de_Judas\" title=\"Epístola de Judas\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Epístola de Judas</a>, Miguel é citado especificamente como \"<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arcanjo\" title=\"Arcanjo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">arcanjo</a>\". Os santuários cristãos em honra a Miguel começaram a aparecer no século IV, quando ele era percebido como um anjo de cura, e, com o tempo, como protetor e líder do exército de Deus contra as forças do mal. Já no século VI, a devoção a São Miguel já havia se espalhado tanto no oriente quanto no ocidente. Com o passar dos anos, as doutrinas sobre ele começaram a se diferenciar.</p><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-weight: bold; margin: 0.3em 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Do_termo_.E2.80.9CArcanjo.E2.80.9D\">Do termo “Arcanjo”</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Miguel_(arcanjo)&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: Do termo “Arcanjo”\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Miguel_(arcanjo)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Editar secção: Do termo “Arcanjo”\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar código-fonte</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">]</span></span></h3><div class=\"thumb tleft\" style=\"float: left; clear: left; margin: 0.5em 1.4em 0.8em 0px; width: auto; border: none; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 182px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Arcangelsinai.jpg\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dd/Arcangelsinai.jpg/180px-Arcangelsinai.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"49\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/dd/Arcangelsinai.jpg 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"261\" data-file-height=\"71\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:Arcangelsinai.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Ampliar\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml%20version%3D%221.0%22%20encoding%3D%22UTF-8%22%20standalone%3D%22no%22%3F%3E%0A%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2011%2015%22%20width%3D%2215%22%20height%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cg%20id%3D%22magnify-clip%22%20fill%3D%22%23fff%22%20stroke%3D%22%23000%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22bigbox%22%20d%3D%22M1.509%201.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22smallbox%22%20d%3D%22M-1.499%206.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fg%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E%0A&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arcanjo\" title=\"Arcanjo\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Arcanjo</a>, num fragmento da Epístola de Judas (Tadeu) no&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Codex_Sinaiticus\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Codex Sinaiticus\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Codex Sinaiticus</a>&nbsp;(330-350 A.D.)</div></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">Arcanjo tem duas raízes, “arch” e “angelos”.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">O prefixo grego “arch” (???) deriva de “arché” (????) que se refere tanto a “começo, ponto de partida, princípio”, como “suprema substância subjacente” ou “princípio supremo indemonstrável”&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-autogenerated2_2-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-autogenerated2-2\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[2]</a></sup>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">A partir dessa raiz “arché” temos o antepositivo “arch”, em português, com o sentido de “aquilo que está na frente, o que está no começo, na origem, ponto de partida de um entroncamento”&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-autogenerated2_2-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-autogenerated2-2\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[2]</a></sup>, sendo traduzido “acima”, “superior” ou “mais importante” e “o que governa, que dirige, que comanda, que lidera” e ainda carregando consigo ideias de poder, autoridade, império e superioridade&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-3\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[3]</a></sup>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">Quanto ao grego “angelos” (???????), vertido para “anjo”, significa simplesmente “mensageiro”.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">A partir dessas raízes, portanto, a palavra “Arcanjo” (??????????) se traduz “Líder dos Mensageiros”, “Chefe dos Mensageiros”&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-4\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[4]</a></sup>&nbsp;\"Capitão dos Anjos\"&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-autogenerated1_5-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-autogenerated1-5\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[5]</a></sup>,\"Primeiro Anjo\"&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-autogenerated1_5-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-autogenerated1-5\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[5]</a></sup>, “Acima dos Anjos”, “Superior aos Anjos”&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-autogenerated2_2-2\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-autogenerated2-2\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[2]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-6\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[6]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-autogenerated4_7-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-autogenerated4-7\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[7]</a></sup>&nbsp;“Anjo Superior”&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-8\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[8]</a></sup>&nbsp;ou “Anjo Chefe”&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-9\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[9]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-10\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[10]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-11\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[11]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-12\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-12\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[12]</a></sup>, num aspecto qualitativo de liderança e substancialmente de superioridade&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-autogenerated4_7-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-autogenerated4-7\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[7]</a></sup>, da mesma maneira que se traduz palavras com o mesmo radical, tal como “arquiteto” (chefe dos construtores), “arcebispo” (classe hierárquica superior a Bispo), “hierarquia” (poder sagrado) ou “anarquia” (falta ou ausência de poder).</p><div class=\"thumb tright\" style=\"clear: right; float: right; margin: 0.5em 0px 0.8em 1.4em; width: auto; border: none; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 182px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:MichaelHebreo.jpg\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d2/MichaelHebreo.jpg/180px-MichaelHebreo.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"86\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d2/MichaelHebreo.jpg/270px-MichaelHebreo.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d2/MichaelHebreo.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"320\" data-file-height=\"153\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ficheiro:MichaelHebreo.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Ampliar\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml%20version%3D%221.0%22%20encoding%3D%22UTF-8%22%20standalone%3D%22no%22%3F%3E%0A%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2011%2015%22%20width%3D%2215%22%20height%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cg%20id%3D%22magnify-clip%22%20fill%3D%22%23fff%22%20stroke%3D%22%23000%22%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22bigbox%22%20d%3D%22M1.509%201.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Cpath%20id%3D%22smallbox%22%20d%3D%22M-1.499%206.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22%2F%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fg%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E%0A&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div>Miguel em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hebraico\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hebraico\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Hebraico</a></div></div></div><h3 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-weight: bold; margin: 0.3em 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.6; font-family: sans-serif;\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Do_termo_.E2.80.9CMiguel.E2.80.9D\">Do termo “Miguel”</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\" style=\"user-select: none; font-size: small; font-weight: normal; margin-left: 1em; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; unicode-bidi: isolate;\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-right: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">[</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Miguel_(arcanjo)&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Editar secção: Do termo “Miguel”\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\" style=\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Miguel_(arcanjo)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Editar secção: Do termo “Miguel”\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">editar código-fonte</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">]</span></span></h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">A tradução literal para o nome Miguel é “Aquele/Quem como Deus”.</p><ul style=\"margin: 0.3em 0px 0px 1.6em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3C%3Fxml%20version%3D%221.0%22%20encoding%3D%22UTF-8%22%3F%3E%0A%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20version%3D%221.1%22%20width%3D%225%22%20height%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Ccircle%20cx%3D%222.5%22%20cy%3D%229.5%22%20r%3D%222.5%22%20fill%3D%22%2300528c%22%2F%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E%0A&quot;); font-size: 14px;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\"><b>Mi</b>&nbsp;= Aquele/Quem(?)</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\"><b>Ka</b>&nbsp;= Como</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.1em;\"><b>El</b>&nbsp;= Deus</li></ul><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">Como no hebraico não existia sinais de pontuação, algumas palavras trariam consigo um significado inquisitivo. Por isso a partícula “Mi” que significa “quem” muitas vezes é traduzida sintaticamente como interrogação, ocorrendo em 350 textos do Antigo Testamento onde é mencionada<sup id=\"cite_ref-13\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-13\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[13]</a></sup>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\"><b>Exemplo</b>:</p><div class=\"citado\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 1em 4em;\">“<i>Depois disto ouvi a voz do Senhor, que dizia: A&nbsp;<b>quem</b>&nbsp;enviarei,&nbsp;<b>e quem</b>&nbsp;irá por nós<b>?</b>&nbsp;Então disse eu: Eis-me aqui, envia-me a mim.</i>” (Is. 6:8)</div><div class=\"citado\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 1em 4em;\">?????? ?????? ???? ??? ????? ?????&nbsp;<b>???</b>&nbsp;??????? ???? ???? ?????? (Texto Original Hebraico)<sup id=\"cite_ref-14\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-14\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[14]</a></sup></div><div class=\"citado\" style=\"font-size: 14px; margin: 1em 4em;\">va\'eshma et qol adonai omer et·<b>mi</b>&nbsp;esh\'laj u<b>mi</b>&nbsp;ielej·lanu vaomar hineni shelajeni ??? (Texto Original Transliterado)<sup id=\"cite_ref-15\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-15\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[15]</a></sup></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">Dessa forma, o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talmude\" title=\"Talmude\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Talmude</a>&nbsp;sugere uma interpretação inquisitiva para o nome Miguel, tendo a tradução contextual “Quem é como Deus?”<sup id=\"cite_ref-autogenerated3_16-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-autogenerated3-16\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[16]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-autogenerated3_16-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-autogenerated3-16\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[16]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-17\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-17\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[17]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-18\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-18\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[18]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-19\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-19\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[19]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-20\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-20\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[20]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-21\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-21\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[21]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-22\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-22\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[22]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-23\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-23\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[23]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-24\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-24\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[24]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-25\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-25\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[25]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-26\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-26\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[26]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-27\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-27\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[27]</a></sup>&nbsp;ou “Quem é semelhante a Deus?”<sup id=\"cite_ref-28\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-28\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[28]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-29\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-29\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[29]</a></sup>&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-30\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-30\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[30]</a></sup>. Este entendimento hoje não é compartilhado somente pela comunidade judaica, pois mais tarde foi incorporado pela cristandade em geral “para não colocar em causa a própria Escritura”, tanto por católicos e evangélicos, como adventistas&nbsp;<sup id=\"cite_ref-31\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap;\"><a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miguel_(arcanjo)#cite_note-31\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">[31]</a></sup>, e também por outras comunidades religiosas, como as testemunhas de Jeová e os islâmicos. Mas para as cosmovisões judaica, jeovista e muçulmana, o pressuposto de não haver nenhuma outra pessoa igual a Deus (Sl. 35:10; 89:8) é literal, implicando sugestivamente a resposta “Ninguém é Igual a Deus” num entendimento retórico.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; font-size: 14px;\">Quanto ao sufixo “El”, é também relacionado de forma regular com nomes significando afirmativamente “Deus” em todos os casos, tal como em&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel\" title=\"Daniel\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Daniel</a>&nbsp;(Deus é Juiz),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emanuel\" title=\"Emanuel\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Emanuel</a>&nbsp;(Deus é Conosco),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ezequiel\" title=\"Ezequiel\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ezequiel</a>&nbsp;(A Força é de Deus),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Samuel\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"Samuel\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Samuel</a>&nbsp;(Chamado pelo Nome de Deus),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gamaliel\" title=\"Gamaliel\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Gamaliel</a>&nbsp;(Deus me Faz o Bem),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ananias\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"Ananias\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ananias</a>&nbsp;(Deus é Clemente),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo%C3%A3o_Evangelista\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"João Evangelista\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">João</a>&nbsp;(A Graça é de Deus),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ismael\" title=\"Ismael\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Ismael</a>&nbsp;(Deus Ouve), etc. Esse entendimento é compartilhado por algumas denominações cristãs trinitarianas e alguns famosos comentaristas bíblicos como Matthew Henry e até o próprio João Calvino, pai da Igreja Congregacional, da Presbiteriana e de muitas outras reformadas, trinitarianos convictos, entendendo o termo segundo a tradução literal. Para esses, diferentemente dos judeus, muçulmanos e testemunhas de Jeová, o Arcanjo Miguel não tem natureza angélica, e sim divina, sendo o próprio Cristo que veio com esse “nome de guerra” fazendo um desafio a Satanás que, desde o princípio, sempre desejou estar acima dos anjos e ser igual ao Criador (Is. 14:12–14).</p></div></div>', 1, 1);
